Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,反手 反手\NBackhand. Backhand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,放高球\NAnd lob.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,正手\NForehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 马蒂 - 干嘛\N- Marty! - What!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有电话 - 跟他说我二十分钟前就走了\N- Phone! - Tell him I left 20 minutes ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不当你的传声筒 自己去接那该死的电话\NI'm not your goddamn messenger! Pick up the goddamn phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟不上 沃利 把白衬衫脱了\NI can't. Wally, take the white shirt off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,白球配白衬衫 看不清\NI can't follow the white ball against the white shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别找借口 孬种才这样找借口\NStop it. You're a fucking sun dodger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我孬种？怎么怕了 怕了？\NOh, yeah? I love you. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我是朱迪\NIt's Judy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 朱迪\NHi, Judy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈病得很重\NYour mother, she's very sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的假的？ - 真的\N- Okay, really? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,她脸色苍白 满嘴胡话\NShe's gray in the face. She's speaking nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她一直喊你 你得赶快回家一趟\NShe's asking for you. You should come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,听上去不行了 你们赶紧叫救护车吧\NSounds really bad. You should probably call an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,谁陪她去啊\NWho's gonna go with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 你这么上心 你陪她去呗\NUh, I don't know. You should probably go since you're so invested.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:05:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 别挂\NHold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他不吃这套\NHe's not buying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他说我断气了\NJust tell him I stopped breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:04.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（至尊马蒂 美国制造）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不行 太严重了 我不能这么说\NAbsolutely not. That's ridiculous. I'm not saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他说你正急着送我去医院\NTell him you're taking me to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我得赶紧把她送去急诊\NOkay, fine. I'll take her to the emergency room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,然后在那儿陪着 天知道要陪多久\Nand sit there and wait for God knows how long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,“你来负责伺候我丈夫 给他喂药”\NAnd you can come here and give my husband his medicine
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,“晚上给他翻身做按摩”\Nand massage his feet all night long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,“跟他说我晕倒了”\NTell him I passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- “天呐 你妈刚刚昏过去了” - 你好啊 小姑娘\N- Oh, my God! Your mother, she just lost consciousness. - Hi, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,“你现在赶紧回家”\NYou've gotta come home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,谁啊\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是我 饭马上好\NHi. Just give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,“朱迪 别闹了行吗”\NI don't know what you want me to say, Judy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,“我正忙着 连午饭都还没吃呢”\NI'm busy. I'm on my lunch break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,“我妈就在你旁边指挥 我都听得见”\NI can hear her whispering. She's right there standing next to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- “我都说她昏过去了”- “别来烦我了”\N- I told you she passed out.- It's annoying me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,跟谁通话呢？\NWho are you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 没人\NOh. I'm not talking to anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,朱迪一直占着电话好久了\NJudy's just been tying up the line for an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你买了点热饭\NI got you some broth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,都凉透了\NIt's ice cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 买饭排了好久 买回来都凉了 - 你都不打草稿？\N- Yeah, 'cause the line was really long at the shop. - Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,信不信我现在打电话去核实？\NSo that's what they'll say if I call down and ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是觉得我骗你\NYou don't believe me? You calling me a liar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你就打电话核实去\NPick up the phone and call them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不过看你怎么打 朱迪在占着电话 - 喔 行\N- You're gonna have to get Judy off the phone first. - Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 朱迪 把电话给我挂掉\NHey, Judy, get off the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,看 这颗是国际乒联标准球\NOkay, this is a normal IATT approved ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:20.15,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【国际乒乓球联合会：1926年成立 主管国际乒乓球赛事和规则】
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,盯紧这颗白球\NTry to follow the white ball against the white.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在白背景下挺难的吧\NAlmost impossible, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你眼珠根本没跟上\NI don't even see your eyes moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我穿白衬衫 你连球都看不到\NIf I'm wearing a white shirt, you can't see the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,换颗橙球试试 这是我自个儿想出来的\NNow, imagine it with an orange ball, which no one's ever thought of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧 你盯得多牢 瞧他那眼神\NSee? You're already following it way better. Look at his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 看见没？ - 嗯 看见了\N- See how his eyes are looking? - Yeah, I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在盯得更紧了\NYou're looking more engaged now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是机遇所在 目前桌上网球界\NSo that's what we wanna do. Right now in the world of table tennis,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:39.08,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【桌球：乒乓球早期在上流场合叫做"桌上网球" 简称"桌球"】
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,为了盯住白球都得穿黑衣\Nyou're obliged to wear black, just so you can follow the white ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 看看这个 这是泰德·贝利 - 他是谁？\N- Look at this. That's Ted Bailey. - Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他曾是英国冠军 世界第一\NThat's ex-number one ranked player in the world right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,已经被我打败了\NHe's the British champion. I've already beat him, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,再看这个\NNow look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,网球界第一杰克·克雷默\NThat's Jack Kramer, number one tennis player.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:51.42,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【杰克·克雷默：40-50年代著名网球手 推动网球精英化】
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有啥区别？ - 他穿的是全白\N- What's the difference there? - He's wearing all white.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,对 一身白 很绅士\NHe's in all white. It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:55.56,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【50年代网球为绅士运动 桌上网球(乒乓球)尚非主流】
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这叫品味 这叫格调 这是卖点\NTo me, that's luxury. To me, that's class. You could sell that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:07:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,马蒂 这种定制球得花不少钱\NMarty, a custom ball like that is gonna cost a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,当然得定制 奇人配奇球\NOf course it's custom. It's an original ball for an original guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这是至尊马蒂牌 不是平庸马蒂牌\NIt's the Marty Supreme ball, not the Marty Normal ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.34,0:08:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你算过成本吗？\NBut what's it gonna cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,钱不重要 咱别抠门\NIt doesn't matter the cost. We can't cheap out on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,花不了多少钱的 加拉尼斯先生\NIt's gonna be nominal, Mr. Galanis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是老说先花钱才能赚钱吗\NYou always said we gotta spend money to make money, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,给我端杯咖啡来\NGet me a cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,没门 让你秘书去弄\NNo. Get your secretary to get ya a cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,南希忙着呢 你去弄吧\NNancy's busy. Just get me a coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,才不 我正像大人那样谈生意\NDad, we're talking like men about business here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我才不给你端咖啡 - 赶紧去给老子端咖啡去\N- I'm not getting ya a cup of coffee. - Get me the damn coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,马蒂 也给你来一杯？\NMarty, you want a coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 不用了 我不碰咖啡因\NNo, I'm all right. I'm not drinking caffeine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,听着\NListen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我感谢你和我儿子的这份交情\NI appreciate you're friends with my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但他不成器\NHe's limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,三十岁还靠爹吃饭\NHe's 30 years old. He's still living at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没啥名堂\NHe hasn't done much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他也不懂做生意 算不清账\NAnd he doesn't know business. He doesn't know the costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我直言 盖拉尼斯先生 我不觉得他不成器\NI don't think he's limited, Mr. Galanis, respectfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,看看您做生意的本事\NI mean, look at your business success.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那是刻在骨子里的 迪翁也有\NThat's in your DNA, and you passed that through to Dion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 只是还没显露出来 - 谁知道呢\N- It just hasn't been awoken yet. - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是没把握\NI wouldn't be here trying to involve you in something that I
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不会拉您入伙的\Ndidn't fully in my bones believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.36,0:09:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我很尊重您的钱 说来您可能不信\NAnd I have tremendous respect for your money. I know it's hard to believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但这门运动在国外是火得不得了\Nbut I'm telling you, this game, it fills stadiums overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在美国火起来也只是时间问题\NAnd it's only a matter of time before it fills stadiums in the United States too,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候我的广告会铺天盖地\Nbefore I'm staring at you from the cover of a Wheaties box.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我对这行一窍不通\NI- I don't know nothing about this business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,确实不通 所以更该信我\NNo, you don't. That's why you gotta trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,下周这个时候 我就是首位赢下英国公开赛的美国人\NThis time next week, I'll be the first American to ever win the British Open.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候我就能一路杀到世锦赛 然后拿下世界第一\NThat'll slide me into the number one ranking for the World Championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候《生活》和《展望》都会报道\NLife magazine's gonna cover it. Look magazine's gonna cover it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是板上钉钉的事 《展望》就在捧我 他们都会捧我\NThey have to. The editor of Look magazine, he loves me. They all love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候我就是这项运动在美国的唯一代言人\NI'm uniquely positioned to be the face of the entire sport in the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:34.87,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（家庭鞋履）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,劳埃德!\NLloyd!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我要关门了\NI'm closing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,看得出来 我来找我叔\NYeah, I can see that. Just here to see my uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他走了\NHe left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:09:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,走了? 什么叫走了? 今天不回来了?\NHe left? What do you mean he left? For the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他得送你妈去医院\NHe had to take your mother to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真是够了 她没病\NFor crying out loud. She's not sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 劳埃德 他欠我钱 咱们本来今天结账的\NHey, Lloyd, he owes me money. We were supposed to settle up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你没去吃那五小时的午饭\NWell, maybe if you didn't take that five-hour lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 兴许就能见着他了 - 闭嘴吧你\N- you would have spoke with him. - Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,听着精神不少啊? 好得挺快嘛\NYou're sounding a lot better, huh? That happened quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我死不了 托你的福!\NI'll live, no thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 妈 你跟默里在一起吗? 实话实说\NEnough, Mom. Are you with Murray? Be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没 我看他出发去旅行了 行吧?\NNo. I think he left for his trip. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,旅行? 什么旅行?\NHis trip? What trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他带埃丝特去库彻度假村过周末了\NHe's taking Esther to Kutchers for the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但只要我开口 他肯定会留下\NBut he would have stayed if I asked him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本没病 妈 他本该给我路费买机票的\NYou're not sick, Mom. He was supposed to give me my money for my flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 宝贝 我对此一无所知\NWell, I don't know anything about that, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你少来! 你以为我为什么要在这儿打工?\NYes, you do! Why do you think I'm working here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.91,0:10:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我接这活儿纯粹就是为了这个\NI literally only accepted this job for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:11:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全听不懂你在暗示什么\NI have no idea what you are implying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你知道这是什么吗? - 什么 这是什么?\N- You know what this is? - What, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这是蓄意破坏 你在整我\NThis is sabotage. You're sabotaging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,得了吧 是你在毁掉你自己的人生\NOh, please. You're sabotaging your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是什么? - 什么?\N- What is that? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你认真的? 觉得我要抢你?\NAre you seriously thinking I'm gonna rob you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,职业反应\NJust a reflex.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是想抢你 你早死在血泊里了\NIf I wanted to rob you, you'd be dead. You'd be in a pool of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来拿西装的 你知道我为了这趟旅行专门买的吗?\NI came to grab my suit. You know I bought this specifically for my trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,还没听说打乒乓球得穿西装\NDidn't know you need a suit to play ping pong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想拿回默里欠我的700美元\NI just want the $700 that Murray owes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,呵 不给呢?\NYeah, or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不然我就往你腿上来一枪 - 你不敢\N- Or I'm gonna shoot you in the leg. - No you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定?\NYou sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你往我腿上开枪 下半辈子就在牢里过吧\NYou shoot me in the leg, you'll be spending the next few years in jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就往你头上开枪\NI'll shoot you in the head instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你也没那胆子\NYou're not gonna do that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 劳埃德 我只要说好的那份 一分都不多要\NLook, Lloyd, I just want what was promised to me, not a penny more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,等我回来 带的奖金会是这个数的十倍\NI'm gonna be coming home with ten times that amount in prize money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所以睁一只眼闭一只眼 让我拿走应得的\NSo just turn the other cheek, let me take what I'm owed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,等我回来 匀给你整整100美元\Nand I'll give you an even $100 dollars when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没兴趣\NNot interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,劳埃德 拜托了 看着我\NLloyd, come on. Look at me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,咱俩都清楚 你巴不得看我卷铺盖走人\NWe both know you'd love nothing more than to see my ass get canned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你干这活儿比我有干劲一千倍\NYou're a thousand times more motivated than me to do this job,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但你瞧瞧这个 行吗?\Nand yet look at this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.69,0:12:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧\NLook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,默里给我的 翻过来\NMurray gave that to me. Flip it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,经理 我要当你上司了!\NManager. I'm gonna be your boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,够不公平吧? 我想开除你就开除你\NHow unfair is that? I could fire you whenever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我还能让你跪地上扫地\NI could tell you to sweep the floor on your hands and knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 爽吗?\NHow about that, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,劳埃德 我现在真拿枪指着你呢\NLloyd, I'm actually pointing a gun at you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我是真的威胁要开火\NI'm actually threatening to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是场如假包换的抢劫 指纹到处都是\NThis is a legit robbery like any other. My fingerprints are all over this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是事实\NThese are facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以开保险箱 拿走我应得的\NSo open the safe, let me take what I'm owed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,完事你打电话给默里 如实禀报\Nand you can call Murray, tell him exactly what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,炒了我 告我都行 随你便 行吗?\Nget me fired, press charges. Whatever you want, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,行\NFine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给您 先生 - 谢了\N- Here you go, sir. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:56.82,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 我偏爱那高峰时分 ♪\N♪ The time I like is the rush hour ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:58.74,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 只因我沉醉那喧嚣 ♪\N♪ 'Cause I like the rush ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:01.91,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 人潮推搡挤动 ♪\N♪ The pushing of the people ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:04.37,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 一切深得我心 ♪\N♪ I like it all so much ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:07.29,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 万物熙攘忙碌 ♪\N♪ Such a mass of motion ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:09.83,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 莫问去向何方 ♪\N♪ Do not know where it goes ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们没有单间吗?\NWe don't get our own rooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿冷得要死\NIt's freezing in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在给我严肃点 盯着我\NI really need you to be serious now. Eyes on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,巴基斯坦 看着我\NPakistan, I need you to look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 日本今年派队来了? 瞧见没?\NWait, Japan brought a team this year? You see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.56,0:13:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 日本人派了一队\NYeah. The Japs sent a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,禁令解除了?\NWhat about the travel ban?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 肯定解禁了 - 不再禁了?\N- They must have lifted it. - No more travel ban?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 先生们 亮下球拍吧\NOkay, gentlemen, I want you to flip your paddles for me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,来了 一 二 三\NHere we go. One. Two. Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,别动\NHold it still.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:45.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 握个手吧 ♪\N♪ Shake hands ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:48.24,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 握个手吧 ♪\N♪ Shake hands ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,赛点 毛瑟\NMatch point, Mauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,获胜 毛瑟\NMatch, Mauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我打太多正手了 应该逼我打反手的\NYou let me get to my forehand too much. Should've tried to put me in my backhand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,得分 远藤\NPoint, Endo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,得分 远藤\NPoint, Endo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:15:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 几比几了? - 19比4\N- What's the score here? - Nineteen-four.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那个日本人? - 日本人把贝利虐惨了\N- The Japanese guy? - Japanese guy's trashing Bailey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他在用什么? 那是什么球拍?\NWhat's he using? What's that paddle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 伙计 谁都没见过\NI don't know, mate. No one knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没声音\NIt's silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 跟幽灵一样! - 哇\N- Like a ghost! - Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,得分 远藤\NPoint, Endo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,赛点\NMatch point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 打得好 马蒂 - 打得好\N- Great game, Marty. - Great game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:15:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,比赛结束 毛瑟胜\NMatch, Mauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,斯德哥尔摩锦标赛的冠军...\NThe winners of the tournament at Stockholm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你就是拉姆·塞西 对吧?\NHey. You're Ram Sethi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 能请你稍等一下吗?\NSorry, could you hold for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不介意吧? - 没事 找我有事吗?\N- You don't mind? - No. Can I help you with something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是好奇 你们在城里住哪儿?\NI was just curious, where are you staying while you're in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你有什么关系?\NWhat business is it of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是问问 你们住哪家酒店?\NI'm just saying, what hotel are you staying at?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,国际乒联的所有代表都住在丽兹酒店\NAll the IATT representatives are stationed at the Ritz.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 丽兹酒店? 嗯 我也听说了 - 是的\N- At the Ritz? Yeah, that's what I heard. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你觉得这合适吗? - 我不懂你在暗示什么\N- Do you think that's okay? - I don't know what you're implying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你见过他们给我安排的地儿吗? - 有问题吗?\N- Have you seen where they put me? - Is it a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我直言 先生 那地方就是个垃圾场\NWell, with all due respect, sir, it's a dump.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真抱歉 那儿没达到您的高标准\NI'm so sorry it doesn't meet your high standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为所有球员提供免费住宿 毛瑟先生\NWe offer complimentary housing to all our players, Mr. Mauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,据我所知 只有你在抱怨\NSo far as I know, you're the only one to complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟我说话的口气 就像我是街边随处可见的球员一样?\NYou're talking to me like I'm any player off the street, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我得休息好 才能赢下锦标赛\NI need good rest so I can win the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你很清楚 美国人夺冠对这项运动意味着什么\NYou know perfectly well what an American win will do for the future of the sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我对乒乓球有好处 塞西先生 - 那就向美乒协反映吧\N- I'm good for table tennis, Mr. Sethi. - Appeal to the USTTA.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,美乒协根本不存在 就在哪弄了张桌子坐了俩人\NThere is no USTTA. The USTTA is two guys and a desk. It doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那不是我的问题 - 这就是你的问题\N- Well, that's not my problem. - It is your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我要住你住的那儿! 那才是我需要的!\NI wanna stay where you're staying! That's what I need!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这次谈话非常无礼\NI am finding this whole exchange really offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你感到冒犯了? - 我感到被冒犯了\N- You're offended? - I am offended.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我还被冒犯了呢! 你让你们的明星球员蜷在耗子洞里!\NI'm offended! You're making your star player huddle in a rat's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真抱歉 刚才被打断了\NI'm so sorry for that interruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 回到锡兰和墨西哥的话题...\NUm, back to Ceylon and Mexico...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这酒店真不赖 肯定得花不少钱 - 是啊 特别棒\N- This is a nice hotel. Must cost a mint. - Yeah, very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,住宿费是国际乒联报销吗?\NThe IATT covers accommodations?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 只给明星球员报销 - 真的吗? 这种球员有几个?\N- Only for their star players. - Is that right? How many are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,明星球员? 我不知道 反正我也没见着别人 所以就我一个\NStar players? I don't know. I haven't seen any others, so one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,进半决赛了 紧张吗?\NAny nerves, going into the semis?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,紧张? 对阵克莱茨基? 开什么玩笑?\NNerves? Against Kletzki? No. You kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.81,0:17:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他可是过去三年的锦标赛冠军\NWell, he's won the tournament for the last three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他名气可不小 - 我的名气也不小\N- He's got quite the reputation. - I have quite the reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 奥斯威辛没办成的事 我要替它办了\NLook, I'm gonna do to Kletzki what Auschwitz couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 我要把这活儿彻底收个尾\NOkay. I'm gonna finish the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.87,0:17:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我的天呐 - 哥们 话说重了点\N- Jesus Christ. - A little strong, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 我是犹太人 我能这么说\NIt's all right. I'm Jewish. I can say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 仔细想想 我就是希特勒最深的梦魇\NIn fact, if you think about it, I'm like Hitler's worst nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这么说?\NAnd why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我 我还在这儿呢\NLook at me. I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我办到了 我站在巅峰 我是希特勒战败后的终极产物\NI did it, I'm on top. I'm the ultimate product of Hitler's defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,行 记下来 这段不错 记下来\NYeah, write that down. That was good. Write that down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 写得好 - "希特勒战败后的终极产物"\N- Nice one. - "Ultimate product of Hitler's defeat."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我就喜欢这种自信 - 把它印在我的照片下面\N- I do like that confidence. - Put that under a picture of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,谈谈你的成长背景吧\N- Tell us a bit about your background. - My background?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不说笑了... 我妈死于难产\NNo, but seriously... My mother died in childbirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸是个赌棍输家 我两岁时他就抛弃了我\NMy father was a compulsive loser who abandoned me when I was two years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我被困在纽约的孤儿院系统里\NI got stuck in the New York City orphanage system,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在一个又一个鬼地方之间被踢来踢去\Ngot shuttled from one hellhole to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 自然也留了案底 - 那不是凯·斯通吗?\N- Naturally, got in trouble with the law. - Isn't that Kay Stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想让那些破事定义我\NI don't want any of that to define me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 借过 啥?\NExcuse me. Excuse me. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 凯·斯通在那儿 - 就是她\N- It's Kay Stone over there. - That's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,谁啊?\NWho's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就那个电影女星 30年代那会儿的\NWell, you know, the movie actress. Like, from the 1930s.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 机缘巧合- 机缘巧合?\N- Opportunities. - Opportunities?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 挺好看的 - 是啊 经典电影\N- That was good. - Yeah, yeah. Great movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 黑匣子- 我爸当年迷死她了\N- Black Box. - My dad loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是啊 - 没错\N- Yeah. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她红过? - 红透半边天\N- She was big? - She was huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,昙花一现 真是她\NCame and went. That's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这就是好莱坞 伙计 - 没错 是她\N- That's Hollywood, mate. - Yeah. It's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,确实是\NIt is indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是有个带湖的名字?\NSomething about a lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 暗影湖- 嗯 那部也不错\N- Shadow Lake. - Yeah, that was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们 你们觉得我有机会吗?\NThink I have a chance, lads?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,下个问题\NNext question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,喂?\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 凯? - 我是\N- Kay? - Speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.58,0:19:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 我是马蒂·毛瑟 我在皇家套房\NHey, it's Marty Mauser. I'm in the Royal Suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨天在大厅见到你了\NI saw you in the lobby yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,行\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我们对上眼了 那会儿我正接受采访呢\NYeah, we made eye contact. I was being interviewed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我没印象\NI don't recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我特别崇拜你\NWell, I'm a huge admirer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 找我有事吗?\NOkay. Can I help you with something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧 我刚才把客房服务菜单全都点了一遍\NMaybe. I just ordered one of everything off the room service menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.22,0:19:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我一个人肯定吃不完\NThere's no way I'll be able to eat it all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\NAh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你想让我去你房间?\NSo you'd like me to come up to your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗯 没错 - 或许我该让我丈夫替我去\N- Mm-hmm. Yeah. - Perhaps I should send my husband instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题 让他上来 我下去找你\NSure. He can come up here, and I'll come down to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.19,0:19:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 妙极 谢谢 再见- 等等 我还想再聊聊\N- Wonderful. Thank you. Goodbye.- Wait. I wanna keep talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?\NWhy is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我还没跟真正的电影明星聊过天\NBecause I've never talked to an actual movie star.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那你现在聊过了 希望这段经历如你所愿\NWell, now you have. I hope the experience was all you thought it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 其实我也算个表演者\NYou know, I'm something of a performer too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是吗?- 对 你不信?\N- Are you?- Yeah. You don't believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我...\NI...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你... 怎么? 说话啊?\NYou... What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你是表演者?\NYou're a performer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我就是 你跟前有每日邮报吗?\NYeah, I am a performer. You got the Daily Mailin front of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 有 确实有\NUh, I do have it, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.38,0:20:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,行 翻到第12页\NOkay. Well, turn to page 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,第12页\NPage 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.76,0:20:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,行 我这看的是什么?\NOkay. What am I looking at here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 就在中间 正中间- 呃\N- Down the middle, in the center.- Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你?\NThis is you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,对 "天选之子" 拍得不错吧?\NYeah, "the chosen one." It's a nice picture, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,乒乓球?\NPing pong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我打乒乓球 来参加全英赛的\NI play table tennis. I'm here competing in the British Open.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你多大? - 我23\N- How old are you? - I'm 23.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,23岁\NTwenty-three.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢说你一部我演的片子都叫不上来\NI bet you can't name one film I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这么说?\NWhat makes you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,因为在你出生前我早已息影了\NBecause I stopped acting before you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.86,0:20:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的吗? 真有意思- 嗯\N- Really? That's really interesting.- Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,凯 你拿我的刮胡刀刮腿毛了?\NKay, did you use my razor to shave your legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,刀片钝了 我都割伤了\NIt's dull. I've cut myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没拿 - 谁在说话? 你丈夫?\N- No. - Who's that? Your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.29,0:20:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,估计是有人偷溜进来拿它劈柴了\NI guess someone must've snuck in and chopped wood with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我正打电话呢 - 操\N- I'm on the phone. - Holy shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 跟谁打? - 黛比\N- With whom? - Debbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 黛比 - 黛比?\N- Debbie. - Debbie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,叫她干点正事\NTell her to get a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他走了吗?- 嗯\N- Is he gone?- Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,行\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 为什么不演戏了? 聊聊这个\NSo, why'd you stop acting? Let's talk about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我真得走了\NYou know, I really have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定怀念片场 吧? 明天来温布利看我比赛\NYou must miss it, don't you? Come watch me play at Wembley tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我... 我去不了\NI... I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,别啊 来亲眼看我把世界第一拉下马\NCome on. You can watch me dethrone the number one ranked player in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我没空\NI'm not available.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.56,0:21:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 是吗? 忙什么呢?\NOh, yeah? What you got going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上 我得陪我丈夫去参加一个大型推广活动\NActually, I have a big promotional event to attend to for my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 这样\NOh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他推广什么?\NWhat's he promoting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.32,0:21:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,钢笔\NPens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 钢笔? 你认真的?- 钢笔\N- Pens? Are you serious?- Pens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 写字用的钢笔?- 对\N- Like, writing pens?- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,啥? 他是个卖笔的?\NWhat, like, he's a pen salesman?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那你们怎么住得起这种套房?\NHow can you afford the suite you're in?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他是洛克威尔墨水公司的老板\NHe owns Rockwell Ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 行吧...\NOh. Okay. Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.75,0:21:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我知道洛克威尔墨水- 我想也是\N- I know Rockwell Ink.- I'm sure you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.17,0:21:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,行\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.71,0:21:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么活动?\NWell, what's the event?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他请了阿加莎·克里斯蒂在哈查兹书店签售\NHe's hired Agatha Christie to sign books at Hatchards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.76,0:21:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\NOoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,听着真无聊\NThat sounds really boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,行\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.44,0:21:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 真是够了\NOh, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.82,0:21:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了? - 先别挂 问你个事\N- What is it? - Don't hang up. Just one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.32,0:21:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你房间对着马路还是院子?\NDoes your room face the street or the courtyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.99,0:22:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我就行 对着马路还是院子?\NJust answer the question. Is it facing the street or the courtyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.16,0:22:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 院子 - 好\N- The courtyard. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.49,0:22:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,去窗户那儿 你住几层?\NI need you to go to the window. What floor are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是三层\NI'm on the third floor, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,三层 好 完美\NThird floor. Okay, perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.71,0:22:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,往街对面看\NLook across the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,看见那扇开着的窗了吗? 桌上还有盘水果\NYou see the open window with a bowl of fruit on the table?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.34,0:22:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,看见了\NI do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.63,0:22:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,看好了 我会让那盘子里凭空多出一个苹果\NHere's what's gonna happen. I'm gonna make an apple appear in that bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.01,0:22:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我办到了 你就推掉你那小约会 来看我比赛\NAnd if I do, you're gonna blow off your little rendezvous and come watch me play.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.76,0:22:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不 我可没答应你什么 不行\NNo, no, no. I'm not agreeing to anything, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用答应 反正我也要做 好了吗? 一...\NYou don't have to agree to anything. I'm gonna do it anyway. Okay? One...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.43,0:22:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,二...\Ntwo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.23,0:22:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,三\Nthree.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.86,0:22:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把票留在售票处\NI'll leave a ticket for you at the box office.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.12,0:23:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,得分 毛瑟\NPoint, Mauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,二十比五\NTwenty to five.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.21,0:23:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,克莱茨基大比分零比二落后毛瑟\NKletzki trails Mauser two games to nil.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.25,0:23:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,局点兼赛点 毛瑟\NGame and match point, Mauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.42,0:23:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这球咱们玩点花活儿 - 好啊\N- Let's have a little fun with this one. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.13,0:23:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 玩点花的 明白? - 收到\N- Have a little fun, all right? - Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.13,0:23:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,换克莱茨基发球\NService switches to Kletzki.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.79,0:24:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,得分 克莱茨基\NPoint, Kletzki.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.01,0:24:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,打得漂亮 先生们 精彩 谢谢\NVery well, gentlemen. Thank you for that. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.80,0:24:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,克莱茨基发球 六比二十\NKletzki serves 6-20.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.14,0:24:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,毛瑟大比分二比零领先\NMauser leads two games to zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.73,0:24:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,再次来到毛瑟先生的赛点\NMatch point again for Mr. Mauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.69,0:24:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,还是你发球 克莱茨基\NYour service again, Kletzki.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.07,0:24:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,得分 毛瑟!\NPoint, Mauser!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.32,0:24:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,毛瑟以二十一比六赢下比赛 总比分三比零\NMauser wins the game and match by 21-6. Three games to nil.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.62,0:24:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,毛瑟晋级决赛 对手是日本的远藤古都\NMauser's on to the finals where he will face Koto Endo of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.67,0:25:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,想吃什么随便点 别看价格 行吗?\NGet whatever you want. Don't even look at the prices, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.01,0:25:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你点什么?\NWhat are you getting?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.88,0:25:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我要惠灵顿牛排和鱼子酱拼盘\NI'm gonna get the Beef Wellington and the caviar tasting plate
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.47,0:25:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这是菜单上最贵的\Nbecause they're the most expensive items on the menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.34,0:25:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 咱们再说回那个哈林篮球队的事\NListen, I would like to keep going back a little bit about the Globetrotters.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.35,0:25:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 又提哈林篮球队? - 对\N- About the Harlem Globetrotters, again? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.93,0:25:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我说了没兴趣 - 为什么不?\N- I told you, I'm not interested. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.47,0:25:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我不想去\N'Cause I don't wanna do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.68,0:25:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,报酬非常高\NIt's great money.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.27,0:25:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们还能环游世界 你见过威尼斯吗?\NAnd we will travel all over the world. Have you seen Venice?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.85,0:25:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想在人家中场休息去厕所的时候\NI don't wanna be doing trick shots for a halftime show
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.81,0:25:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在场上表演杂耍球\Nwhile people are going to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.44,0:25:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那太跌份了 行吗?\NThat's beneath me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.53,0:25:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那待遇可是皇室级别的 - 服务员在哪儿呢?\N- They're treated like royalty. - Where's the waiter?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.36,0:25:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 听着 我认识干过这行的人 - 打扰下\N- Listen, I know people who have done this. - Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.11,0:25:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,借过\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.28,0:25:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个绝佳的机会 我们不该错过\NIt's a great opportunity. We should not miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.12,0:25:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,马蒂\NMarty.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.46,0:25:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 先生 有什么能帮您的?\NYes, sir. May I help you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.96,0:25:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 我们可以点菜了吗?\NHi. Can we order?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.04,0:25:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 先生 我这就叫服务员过来\NOf course, sir. Let me fetch your waiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.71,0:25:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 等会 - 请说\N- Hang on. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.26,0:25:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 今晚洛克威尔先生那桌我买单\NUh, I'll be taking care of the Rockwell tab tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.34,0:25:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,记我账上 皇家套房 马蒂·毛瑟\NPut it on my room. The Royal Suite. Marty Mauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.97,0:25:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 记清楚 告诉他们是我买的单 - 明白 交给我吧 先生\N- And make sure they know it's me, too. - I will. Leave it to me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.47,0:25:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别让他们拒绝 - 没问题\N- Don't take no for an answer. - I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.93,0:25:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 马蒂·毛瑟 皇家套房 去告诉他们 - 好的 先生\N- Marty Mauser. Royal Suite. Go tell 'em. - Will do, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.06,0:26:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 看着我 别往那儿瞅 看着我\NOkay. Look at me. Don't look there. Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.19,0:26:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 洛克威尔是谁? - 一个蠢货\N- Who's Rockwell? - Some bozo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.44,0:26:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,现在看过去 自然点 他在干嘛?\NLook over now. Be subtle about it. What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.15,0:26:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 他以前没来过这儿\NHe hasn't been here before, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.03,0:26:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他在看咱们\NHe's looking at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.20,0:26:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的? - 真的\N- Really? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.28,0:26:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,行 继续跟我聊 自然点\NOkay, keep talking to me. Be normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.62,0:26:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你再考虑考虑\NI want you to reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.66,0:26:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们会是绝佳搭档 我想跟你一块儿干\NWe would be a great team. I wanna do this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.45,0:26:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛非盯着哈林篮球队不放?\NWhy are you so fixed on the Harlem Globetrotters?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.12,0:26:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他们干的事挺可悲的 明白吗?\NIt's very sad what they do, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.25,0:26:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,地球上顶尖的运动员 沦落到去演马戏小丑\NSome of the premier athletes on the planet reduced to acting like circus clowns.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.42,0:26:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在干嘛呢?\NWhat's he doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.71,0:26:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,其实 他正朝咱们走过来\NActually, he's coming towards us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.30,0:26:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 自然点 随意些 - 行 好的 明白\N- Just be normal. Act casual. - Okay, fine. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.39,0:26:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我认得你吗?\NExcuse me. Do I know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.31,0:26:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没\NMm-mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.39,0:26:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我看并不认得\NI don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.60,0:26:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那你想帮我们整桌买单?\NAnd you wanna buy dinner for my entire table tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.89,0:26:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 没意见吧? - 为什么?\N- Yeah. Is it okay? - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.39,0:26:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,什么叫为什么? 我还需要理由?\NWhat do you mean, why? Do I need a reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.82,0:26:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我换个问法 你想要什么?\NLet me rephrase that. What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.32,0:26:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我什么都不要 这只是我表达谢意的一点小法子\NNo, I don't want anything. It's just my small way of saying thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.19,0:26:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢我? - 对\N- Thank you? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.65,0:26:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,具体谢我什么呢?\NThank me for what, specifically?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.28,0:26:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,谢您的那些产品\NFor all your products.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.82,0:26:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 要是没有钢笔 我们该怎么办?\NI mean, where would we be without pens?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.45,0:27:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我才艺不少 但我最自豪的一点\NYou know, I have many talents, but the one I'm most proud of
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.87,0:27:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就是能闻出几里外的屁话--\Nis the ability to smell bullshit from a mile away--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.33,0:27:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是十足真诚的\NI'm being completely sincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.55,0:27:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你哪儿人? - 纽约的 你呢?\N- Where are you from? - New York. What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.09,0:27:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,也是纽约 你干哪行的?\NNew York too. What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.76,0:27:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个职业运动员\NI'm a professional athlete.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.34,0:27:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的? 什么项目? - 乒乓球\N- Really? What sport? - Table tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.60,0:27:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,乒乓球? 那也算运动?\NTable tennis? That's a sport?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.93,0:27:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是了 我是来参加全英赛的\NOf course it is. I'm here competing in the British Open.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.97,0:27:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我明天要在温布利打决赛\NI'm playing at Wembley tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.14,0:27:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,观众满座 对手是日本\Nin front of a sold-out crowd in the finals against Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.94,0:27:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我代表美国出战\NI'm here representing the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.48,0:27:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 慢着 日本? 日本也派队来了?\NWait, wait, wait. Japan? Japan has a team here?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.94,0:27:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我刚就这么说的 - 他们是怎么避开旅行禁令的?\N- That's what I just said. - How'd they get around the travel ban?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.19,0:27:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因为乒乓球是亚洲增长最快的运动\NBecause table tennis is the fastest growing sport in Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.49,0:27:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在那边火得不行\NIt's huge over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.11,0:27:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 这个你肯定感兴趣\NOh, you're gonna like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.20,0:27:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他们管那种握法叫什么吗? 就拿球拍的姿势?\NDo you know what they call their grip? The way they hold their rackets?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.62,0:27:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不知道 - 他们管那叫直拍\N- No. - They call it penholder.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.62,0:27:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎样?\NSo what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.70,0:27:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以用这招啊\NYou can use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.08,0:27:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,拿来干嘛?\NUse it for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.16,0:27:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,搞广告之类的 我哪知道 你才是生意人\NFor an advertisement or something. I don't know, you're the business guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.08,0:27:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我失礼了 这位是我的搭档 克莱茨基\NI'm being rude. This is my associate, Béla Kletzki.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.50,0:27:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,幸会 先生\NNice to meet you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.59,0:27:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜你也是乒乓球手?\NI assume you're a table tennis player also?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.88,0:27:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 没错 其实我是35到39年的世界冠军\NI am. I am. Actually, I was the World Champion from '35 to '39.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.26,0:27:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他曾是世界冠军 我今天赢了他\NHe was the World Champion. I beat him today.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.05,0:27:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他赢了我 但他比我年轻得多\NHe beat me. But he's much younger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.89,0:28:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我比他强得多 更有天赋\NI'm much better than him, much more talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.64,0:28:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我不禁注意到这个纹身 你进过集中营 没错吧?\NI can't help but notice this tattoo. You were in one of the camps, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.69,0:28:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,奥斯威辛-比克瑙 没错 怎么问这个?\NAuschwitz-Birkenau. Yeah. Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.48,0:28:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我儿子为了解放你们丢了命\NMy son lost his life liberating you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.90,0:28:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,节哀顺变\NI'm sorry for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.40,0:28:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为你们是被苏联人解放的\NI thought you were liberated by the Soviets.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.24,0:28:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 确实是 - 并不是美国人\N- We were. - It wasn't the Americans.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.70,0:28:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是按字面意思说的 他在南太平洋服役\NI didn't mean it literally. He was serving in the South Pacific.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.54,0:28:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那他怎么了?\NWell, what happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.75,0:28:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思? 他牺牲了\NWhat do you mean? He was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.79,0:28:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这很好笑?\NYou find that funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.88,0:28:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 天呐 不是 我有时一紧张就会发笑\NOh, God. No, I just get nervous laughter sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.92,0:28:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这算慰藉的话\NIf it's any consolation,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.13,0:28:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我明天会往他们头上投第三颗原子弹\NI'll be dropping a third atom bomb on their heads tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.72,0:28:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我敢说他老妈肯定深感慰藉\NYeah, I'm sure his mother's gonna get a lot of comfort
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.76,0:28:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你打乒乓球纪念他呢\Nthat you're playing ping pong in his honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.47,0:28:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没多大事 但我心领了\NIt's not that big of a deal, but I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.72,0:28:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他-- 他以前替纳粹拆炸弹\NTell him-- He used to diffuse bombs for the Nazis.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.43,0:28:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他你跟我讲过的那个故事--\NTell him the story you told me about--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.19,0:28:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有一桌子客人在等呢\NI've got a whole table of people waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.60,0:28:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 慢着 你肯定会喜欢这故事 告诉他\NWait, wait. You're gonna love this story. Tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.56,0:28:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想听吗? - 并不想 但说吧\N- You wanna hear it? - Not really, but go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.65,0:28:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不 告诉他 特别精彩\NNo, tell him. It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.19,0:28:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,行 我长话短说 那就是...\NOkay, I'll make it quick. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.90,0:28:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚进集中营的时候 被分到了住处\Nwhen I first got to the camp, I was put into housing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.72,0:29:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,走运的是 有个军官认出了我\NLucky for me, there was an officer who recognized me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.62,0:29:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他在1935年布拉格世锦赛上见过我\NHe had seen me in 1935 at the World Championships in Prague.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.33,0:29:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙是个真球迷 懂吗? 铁杆粉\NThis guy was a real fan. I mean, a real fan, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.04,0:29:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说他让你活命是因为你会打乒乓?\NYou're telling me he let you live because you played ping pong?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.63,0:29:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他们尊重我的球技 没错\NThey respected my skills, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.22,0:29:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,后来 他们教我如何拆解SC炸弹\NSo then, they taught me how to dismantle SC bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.14,0:29:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,行吗?\NOkay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.22,0:29:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,每天早上 他们都派我带着炸弹进树林\NEach morning, they would send me into the woods with the bombs
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.81,0:29:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就在集中营外围 在那儿就算炸了也只能伤到我自己\Non the outskirts of the camp where I could only do damage to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.48,0:29:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有一回\NSo one time,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.73,0:29:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟着一只蜜蜂\NI followed a honeybee.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.40,0:29:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,蜜蜂?\NA bee?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.65,0:29:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,一只蜜蜂\NA honeybee,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.24,0:29:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一直跟到它的蜂巢\Nall the way to its hive.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.79,0:29:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我用烟把蜜蜂全都熏走了\NAnd I smoked all the bees out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.87,0:29:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,然后把巢砸开\NAnd then broke it open,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.29,0:29:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我把蜂蜜抹在胸口 胳膊 全身上下都是\Nand I smeared the honey all over my chest, my arms, everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.00,0:29:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.09,0:29:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,因为在那天深夜\N'Cause later that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.80,0:30:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我让铺友们把蜂蜜从我身上舔掉 补充营养\NI let all my bunk mates to lick the honey off of me for nourishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.28,0:31:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,正面\NHeads.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.41,0:31:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 操 - 远藤 选什么?\N- Fuck. - Endo, choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.99,0:31:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,发球\NServe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.37,0:31:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我去那头\NI'll go to that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.88,0:32:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 右手边... - 加油 马蒂! 上啊!\N- On my right... - Come on, Marty! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.96,0:32:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...来自美国的马蒂·毛瑟 世界排名第二\N...Marty Mauser of the United States, ranked second,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.63,0:32:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,对阵来自日本的远藤古都 无排名\Nversus Koto Endo of Japan, unranked.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.10,0:32:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,比赛采取五局三胜制\NThe gentlemen will battle to the best of five
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.35,0:32:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,每局21分\Nin games to 21 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.39,0:32:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,每局须赢至少两分\NEach game shall be won by at least two points.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.69,0:32:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,祝二位好运\NGood luck, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.98,0:32:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,请安静\NQuiet, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.82,0:32:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,开始!\NAll right!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.79,0:32:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,得分 远藤 1-0\NPoint, Endo. One-nil.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.38,0:32:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 美国队!\NCome on, America!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.26,0:32:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,得分 远藤 2-0\NPoint, Endo. Two-nil.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.77,0:32:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好球 马蒂!\NAll right, Marty!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.60,0:32:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊 马蒂!\NCome on, Marty!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.44,0:33:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,得分 远藤 3-0\NPoint, Endo. Three-nil.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.16,0:33:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,得分 远藤 4-0\NPoint, Endo. Four-nil.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.34,0:33:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 马蒂!\NCome on, Marty!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.09,0:33:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,得分 远藤 5-0\NPoint, Endo. Five-nil.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.06,0:33:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,换毛瑟发球\NService switches to Mauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.52,0:33:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,得分 毛瑟\NPoint, Mauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.11,0:33:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,9比19发球\NNine serving 19.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.21,0:34:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,得分 毛瑟 10-19\NPoint, Mauser. 10-19.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.47,0:34:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮 马蒂!\NOkay, Marty!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.99,0:34:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,得分 远藤 20-10\NPoint, Endo. 20-10.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.08,0:34:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,局点\NGame point.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.88,0:34:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,发球\NGo! Serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.86,0:35:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,得分 远藤 21-10\NPoint, Endo. 21-10.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.86,0:35:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,本局远藤胜\NGame, Endo.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.49,0:35:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,远藤大比分二比零领先\NEndo leads two games to zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.41,0:35:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,得分 毛瑟\NPoint, Mauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.46,0:35:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,18-16\NEighteen-16.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.10,0:35:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,得分 毛瑟 17-18\NPoint, Mauser. 17-18.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.27,0:35:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊 马蒂! 加油!\NGo, Marty! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.44,0:35:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,换毛瑟发球\NService switches to Mauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.70,0:36:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,操\NFuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.46,0:36:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,得分 远藤 17-19\NPoint, Endo. 17-19.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.06,0:36:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,操 妈的\NOh, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.90,0:36:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,得分 远藤 17-20\NPoint, Endo. 17-20.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.78,0:36:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,赛点\NAnd match point.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.95,0:36:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,请安静\NQuiet, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.62,0:36:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,安静 坐稳了\NQuiet. Settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.84,0:36:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,毛瑟发球\NYour service, Mauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.84,0:36:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊 马蒂!\NCome on, Marty!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.01,0:37:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,操\NFuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.73,0:37:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不行! 狗屁! 不行!\NNo, bullshit! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.64,0:37:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我要立刻重赛 必须用标准硬板拍!\NI want a rematch right now with a standard-league hard-bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.31,0:37:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没法接受!\NThat is unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.52,0:37:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我安只机械手呢?\NWhat if I had a mechanical arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.19,0:37:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在球上抹胶水行不行? 这样合规吗?\NWhat if I put glue on the ball? Would that be kosher?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.32,0:37:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他全程都在接受场外指导! 我没法接受!\NWhy, he was getting coached the entire time! That is unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.45,0:37:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我打的是真刀真枪的乒乓球! 真乒乓球!\NI play real table tennis! Real table tennis!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.49,0:37:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,简直荒唐\NUnbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.00,0:37:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,简直离谱\NUnbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.08,0:37:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...来自日本的全英赛冠军...\N...British Open champion from Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.42,0:37:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,去你妈的!\NFuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.50,0:37:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...远藤古都!\N...Koto Endo!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.48,0:39:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,您这儿有米尔顿 洛克威尔的预约吗?\NDo you have a Milton Rockwell reservation?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.40,0:39:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 打扰下?- 麻烦查下米尔顿 洛克威尔的预约\N- Excusez-moi?- Milton Rockwell reservation, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.69,0:39:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 洛克威尔?\NAh, Rockwell?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.78,0:39:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 马蒂 我想亲口谢你\NSo, listen, Marty, I wanna personally thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.20,0:39:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你带我接触乒乓球\Nfor introducing me to table tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.28,0:39:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我压根儿没想到 这玩意在亚洲火成这样\NI had no idea what a phenomenon it was in the Asias.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.95,0:39:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦 没错 我知道 - 在日本也大受欢迎!\N- Oh, yeah. I know. - And how big it is in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.79,0:39:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前就想跟你说 场面大得很\NThat's what I was trying to tell you. It's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.58,0:39:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我打算把它加入到推广活动里\NSo, I'm thinking of incorporating it into some of the promotional events
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.29,0:39:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,今年秋天我们在那边正好有活动\Nwe're gonna be doing over there in the fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.38,0:39:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么弄? 你有什么想法?\NHow so? What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.76,0:39:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我想搞一场表演赛\NWhat I wanna do is stage an exhibition match
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.51,0:39:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就在世锦赛期间 让你跟远藤对打\Naround the time of the World Championships between you and Endo.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.18,0:39:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗯 - 我想你会喜欢的\N- Mmm. - I think you'd like that idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.19,0:39:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想给你开个价\NSo I'm gonna make you an offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.52,0:39:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一千美元酬劳\NI'll pay you a thousand dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.56,0:39:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,安排你住东京的帝国饭店\NI'll put you up at the Imperial Hotel in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.19,0:39:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你从纽约出发 还可以坐我的私人飞机\NAnd if you're leaving from New York, I'll give you a seat on my private plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.06,0:39:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,让你这辈子头一回体验把什么叫奢华\Nand you'll fly in luxury for the first time in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.27,0:40:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,行 价钱晚点再谈\NOkay, we can negotiate my price later.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.65,0:40:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是在赛前还是赛后?\NBut this would be before or after the tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.40,0:40:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 开赛前一周左右 - 不行 必须是赛后\N- About a week before the event. - No, it's gotta be after.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.20,0:40:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真刀真枪干之前 我不能在公众面前跟他过招\NI can't face off against the guy in public before it actually counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.37,0:40:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我很看重戏剧张力 这种张力不能被削弱\NDrama is very important to me. I can't undercut the drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.89,0:40:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们别纠结这种细节\NLet's not get tied up in minutiae.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.31,0:40:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想确认下 你是否有兴趣参加\NI just want to find out if you're interested in participating.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.25,0:40:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 当然 任何能展示我天赋的机会我都有兴趣\NOh, yeah. Of course. I'm interested in any opportunity to show off my talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.16,0:40:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不用担心 因为这一次我会彻底碾碎他\NAnd you don't have to worry either, 'cause this time I'm gonna obliterate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.98,0:40:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,主要是球拍的问题\NIt's really the racket that I'm playing,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.67,0:40:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但我保证 准能赢\Nbut I can assure you, it's gonna be a victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.30,0:40:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 听着 我得让你明白这是怎么回事\NOkay, listen. I need you to understand what this thing's about.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.51,0:40:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是正式比赛\NThis is not an official match.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.09,0:40:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,连真球都算不上\NIt's not even a real game.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.84,0:40:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这纯粹是商业推广 为了讨好日本佬\NThis is purely promotional, to entertain the Japanese people,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.01,0:40:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好让他们多买我的笔 懂吗?\Nso they buy more of my pens, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.93,0:40:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你上去打几局 表现出色点\NYou're gonna play a few games. You're gonna be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.65,0:40:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但你不能打得比远藤好 - 你想让我打假球?\N- But you can't play better than Endo. - You want me to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.44,0:40:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,马蒂 给你看个东西\NMarty, let me show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.11,0:40:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,日本最大的杂志\NBiggest magazine in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.49,0:40:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是你让远藤成了国民英雄\NYou made Endo a national treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.16,0:40:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 听着-- - 给我看这个干嘛?\N- Listen-- - Why are you showing me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.45,0:40:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得看了这个我会想输? 这只会让我更想赢\NDo you think this makes me wanna lose? This makes me wanna win.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.16,0:40:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候 输了才是赢\NSometimes, when you lose you're a winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.04,0:40:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 听我解释-- - 我比远藤强一万倍\N- Let me explain. Let me explain. - I'm ten trillion times better than Endo.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.46,0:41:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂吧? 我是输在那该死的球拍上\NYou understand that, right? It's the racket that beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.42,0:41:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他就是个平庸球手 - 我一点都不在乎\N- He's a mediocre player. - I couldn't care less.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.13,0:41:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎乒乓球 这是场戏\NI don't care about table tennis. This is theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.34,0:41:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你担心什么? - 我的名声\N- What are you worried about? - My reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.88,0:41:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的名声? - 没错 我的名声\N- Your reputation? - Yes, my reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.47,0:41:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想为了你把名声扫地 没门\NI don't wanna throw my reputation in the trash for you. I'm not doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.93,0:41:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在不就是在搞那种马戏团式的杂耍吗?\NAren't you playing in a vaudeville circus act right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.60,0:41:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,什么杂耍? 把话说清楚\NWhat do you mean, vaudeville? Finish that sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.85,0:41:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你什么意思? - 你就是个中场余兴节目 马蒂\N- What are you implying? - You're the halftime show, Marty.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.15,0:41:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是哈林篮球队! 地球上顶尖的运动员\NOf the Harlem Globetrotters! The finest athletes on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.23,0:41:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,从一月到现在 至少有八万观众看过我的表演\NI've probably played in front of 80,000 people since January.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.78,0:41:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这很好笑?\NThat's funny to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.11,0:41:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我觉得你整个人都很滑稽\NNo. You're funny to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.53,0:41:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我滑稽? 知道我觉得什么滑稽吗?\NI'm funny to you? You know what's funny to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.32,0:41:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么低三下四去讨好日本人\NThat you want to entertain the Japanese so badly,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.33,0:41:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,而他们杀了你儿子 这才叫滑稽\Nand they murdered your son. That's funny to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.00,0:41:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 咱俩互戳了痛点 扯平了 行吗?\NLook, you struck a nerve, I struck a nerve. Okay? Now we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.05,0:41:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,滚出去\NGet out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.93,0:41:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,别啊 你得先把欠我的那顿饭结了\NNah, I think you owe me a meal first.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.73,0:42:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"小星星"!\N"Twinkle Twinkle Little Star"!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.38,0:42:24.63,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 每个人终究都要学着长大 ♪\N♪ And everybody's gotta learn sometime ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.76,0:42:31.26,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 每个人终究都要学着长大 ♪\N♪ Everybody's gotta learn sometime ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.10,0:42:37.27,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,- ♪ 每个人终究都要学着长大 ♪- 漂亮 教练!\N- ♪ Everybody's gotta learn sometime ♪- Yeah, Coach, yeah!
