Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.60,0:55:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道什么叫憋尿吗 沃利? 不知道?\NDo you know what continence is, Wally? No?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.31,0:55:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,每次我撒尿的时候 我都会憋住\NEvery time I take a piss, I pull back,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.69,0:55:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,憋住 默数到十个数\NI hold my urine in, and I count to ten Mississippi.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.94,0:55:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,锻炼肌肉就得靠这个\NThat's how you build up the muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.19,0:55:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你那是他妈的找膀胱炎呢\NThat's how you get a fuckin' bladder infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.61,0:55:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛呢? 那是我的信\NWhat are you doing? That's my mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.70,0:55:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗?\NAre you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.74,0:55:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你得去买那些该死的尿布\NYou need to grab them goddamn diapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.28,0:55:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不去\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.37,0:55:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,给我清醒点\NAnd get a fucking grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.70,0:55:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不当什么爹\NI'm not a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.14,0:55:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哟 马蒂 - 怎么?\N- Yo, Marty. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.39,0:55:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,丽兹酒店是哪出?\NWhat's the Ritz?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.48,0:55:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛?\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.56,0:55:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你收到一张1500美元的罚单\NYou got a $1,500 fine
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.02,0:55:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,国际乒联发来的...\Nfrom the International Table Tennis...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.15,0:55:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 啥? - ...说是协会要...\N- What? - ...Association and...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.77,0:55:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还要... - 拿进来给我!\N- And they... - Bring it in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.86,0:56:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还要把你这弱鸡给禁赛了 - 拿给我\N- And they banned your scrawny ass. - Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.36,0:56:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这他妈怎么回事?\NWhat the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.12,0:56:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧? - 你他妈又是谁?\N- Are you okay? - Who the fuck are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.49,0:56:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐! 救命! 把这鬼玩意儿从我身上挪开!\NGod! Help me! Get this fucking thing off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.46,0:56:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我的狗!\NMy dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.04,0:56:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 操! - 见鬼! 发生什么了?\N- Holy shit! - Shit! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.42,0:56:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,快点! 从那破浴缸里滚出来帮帮我!\NCome on! Get outta that fuckin' tub and help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.22,0:56:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我的狗快淹死了 伙计 快啊! 帮帮我!\NMy dog's drowning, man. Come on! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.05,0:56:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,行 我把它翻过来 把手抽出来\NOkay, I'm flipping it. Take your arm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.60,0:56:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一 二 - 把它抬开!\N- One. Two. - Lift it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.10,0:56:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,三\NThree.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.77,0:56:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,快把手抽出来! 噢我的天! 我的天!\NTake your arm out! Oh, my God! Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.81,0:56:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,操! 操!\NFuck! Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.94,0:56:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 妈的 你的手\NOh, fuck, your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.90,0:56:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,往后靠 往后靠 别看伤口\NLean back. Lean back. Don't look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.07,0:56:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我得弄个止血带 - 噢 操!\N- I need to make a tourniquet. - Oh, fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.78,0:56:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 过来 手给我 - 你要干嘛?\N- Come here. Give me your arm. - What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.36,0:56:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你干什么? - 手给我\N- What are you doing? - Give me your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.70,0:56:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 妈的 - 我的狗呢?\N- Fuck. - Where's my dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.16,0:56:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,别管那狗了! 手给我\NDon't worry about the dog! Give me your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.58,0:56:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 摩西 - 别乱动 别乱动\N- Moses. - Do nothing. Do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.83,0:56:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,有我在呢 别担心\NI got you. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.29,0:56:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,沃利 快叫救护车!\NWally, call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.29,0:56:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还好吧? - 不 我一点也不好\N- Are you good? - No, I'm not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.54,0:56:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我的眼镜呢?\NWhere are my glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.63,0:57:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我是问你伤着没? 你刚把地板砸穿了\NI mean, are you hurt? You just fell through the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.50,0:57:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真他妈扯淡 我得把钱要回来\NFucking horseshit. I'm getting our money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.67,0:57:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,把钱要回来?\NGetting our money back?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.47,0:57:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,马蒂 咱们得赶紧溜 这才两块五毛钱 你在说啥呢?\NMarty, we gotta get the fuck out of here. It's $2.50. What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.30,0:57:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回来的可不止两块五 你没见刚才发生了什么?\NI'm asking for way more than $2.50. You see what just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.52,0:57:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在这等着 等着\NWait here. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.56,0:57:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 等多久? - 十秒钟\N- For how long? - Ten seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.44,0:57:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我的鞋 我的衣服\NMy shoes, my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.52,0:57:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,全湿透了 里面乱成一团\NEverything's soaking wet. It's a mess in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.69,0:57:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你给我闭嘴吧 - 你想练练?\N- Why don't you put a sock in it? - You wanna switch?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.28,0:57:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你! 我... 我早说了别用他妈的喷淋\NYou! I... I told you not to use the fucking shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.24,0:57:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你才没说 是你把房租给我的 懂吗?\NNo, you didn't. You're the one that rented me the room, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.83,0:57:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我从天花板掉下来差点摔断脖子\NI could have broken my neck falling out of that ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.16,0:57:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的现在也还没准能摔断呢\NThat can fucking still happen too.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.79,0:57:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你现在是在威胁我吗? - 对 没错\N- Are you threatening me right now? - Yeah, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.33,0:57:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 居然敢威胁我? - 对\N- You want to threaten me? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.50,0:57:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 地下室锁了! - 谁拿的他妈的钥匙?\N- Basement is locked! - Who's got the fucking key?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.33,0:57:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 哥们! 听好了! 我要把房钱拿回来...\NListen, man! Listen! I want my money for my room...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.17,0:57:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 救护车来了 - ...我还要赔偿\N- Ambulance. - ...and I want a reimbursement
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.71,0:57:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我那些毁了的破烂儿 - 认真的吗?\N- for my shit that got ruined. - Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.09,0:57:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你那些破玩意儿一个子儿也拿不回来\NYou're not gonna get your shit back.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.30,0:57:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 七块五! - 你什么也别想拿\N- $7.50! - You'll get nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.34,0:57:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快点 帮帮我! - 医护人员来了\N- Come on. Help me! - Paramedics.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.59,0:57:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了 你们可来了 - 病人在哪儿?\N- Good, you're here. - Where's the patient at?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.05,0:57:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在那儿 手臂受伤了 流了好多血\NHe's in here. It's his arm. He's lost a lot of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.89,0:57:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事?\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.35,0:57:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 浴缸砸他身上了 - 浴缸砸他身上了?\N- Bathtub fell on him. - Bathtub fell on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.23,0:57:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我手没知觉了\NI can't feel my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.69,0:57:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哟 吉米 拜托 帮我把这狗弄走\NYo, Jimmy. Come on, you gotta help me with this dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.81,0:58:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我这儿没人手 - 得送它去兽医那儿\N- I don't got nobody free. - We gotta get him to the vet.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.02,0:58:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我现在真腾不出人手 - 它是我的家人 哥们\N- I got nobody free right now. - He's my family, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.44,0:58:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 把两块五还我 我就走 七块五不要了\NListen, now. Just give me the $2.50, and I'll get outta here. Forget the $7.50.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.53,0:58:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把两块五给我就行 - 我帮不了你\N- Just give me $2.50. - I can't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.86,0:58:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,明天找老板去\NSee the owner tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.03,0:58:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 小子 - 都是因为这破旅馆的烂天花板\N- Kid. - It's your shitty ceiling
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.12,0:58:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给闹的 - 小子 噢!\N- in this crummy hotel. - Kid. Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.08,0:58:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我什么都不会给你 - 什么?\N- I ain't giving you nothing. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.16,0:58:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,小子 拜托 把狗送去兽医那儿\NKid. Come on. Just bring the dog to the vet.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.66,0:58:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 我得工作 有活要干\NI can't. I got work. I got a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.46,0:58:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不能被开除 - 你有工作?\N- I can't get fired. - You got a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.58,0:58:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我出双倍工钱 - 不 行不通 不行\N- I'll give you double what you're getting. - No, I can't. I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.75,0:58:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我给三倍 来吧\NI'll give you triple. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.96,0:58:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 悠着点 冷静下 - 行吧\N- Take it easy. Calm down. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.42,0:58:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,行 翻下那个包 看到椅子上的包了吗?\NOkay, look in that bag. See the bag on the chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.59,0:58:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,对 翻那个包 把它打开\NYeah, go in that bag, okay? Open it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.55,0:58:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我得给你上个止血带\NI'm gonna apply a tourniquet to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.14,0:58:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我这就把原来那个撤了\NI'm gonna remove the other tourniquet right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.97,0:58:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,拿五十给你自己 没错\NTake 50 for yourself. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.10,0:58:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,再带五十给兽医 明白吗?\NBring 50 for the vet, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.31,0:58:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,血都喷出来了\NWe got blood squirting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.56,0:58:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他在13街和1大道交口\NHe's on 13th and 1st.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.10,0:58:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他我一完事就赶过去 懂吗?\NAnd tell him I'll be there as soon as I can get there, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.77,0:58:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你居然要给这混蛋钱?\NYou're gonna give this motherfucker money?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.82,0:58:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是他他妈让浴缸砸到你身上的\NHe's the one who fuckin' dropped the tub on ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.65,0:58:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我警告过他别进那个破浴缸的\NI told him not to get in the fuckin' bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.36,0:58:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,真他妈讲究 小子\NFucking mensch, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.91,0:58:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,担架准备好了吗? 咱们送他去贝尔维尤\NStretcher ready? We'll take him to Bellevue.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.57,0:58:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真他妈讲究\NFucking mensch.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.66,0:58:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们现在掉头还来得及\NWe can still turn around
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.99,0:58:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能送他去兽医那儿 - 不行 不行\N- and take him to the vet. - No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.83,0:58:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 五十块钱绰绰有余了 - 知道什么比五十块更好吗? 一百块\N- Fifty dollars is more than enough. - You know what's better than 50? 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.92,0:59:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有一百块本钱 咱们能赢个盆满钵满\NWe can clean house with a hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.38,0:59:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,别贪得无厌了 你这该死的犹太佬\NDon't be greedy, you fucking Jew.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.00,0:59:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 是1500美元的罚款 是你拿给我看的\NNo, no. It's a $1,500 fine. You're the one that showed it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.92,0:59:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便说下 咱们得连续两周每晚都这么干\NBy the way, we gotta do this every night for two weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.09,0:59:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 否则我就去不了日本了 - "咱们"? 噢 不不不\N- or else I can't go to Japan. - "We"? Oh, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.68,0:59:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想因为你捅了娄子就两周不去上班\NI'm not taking two weeks off work 'cause you fucked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.97,0:59:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 拿着这个 伙计\NHey. Take this, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.05,0:59:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着 没错 好孩子\NTake this. There you go. Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.68,0:59:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,把这混蛋的项圈松一松 伙计\NLoosen up the collar on this motherfucker, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.35,0:59:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 行了 - 他听着像个破暖气片\N- All right. - He sound like a radiator.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.19,0:59:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们先去打球\NWe're gonna go play,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.27,0:59:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,回来的路上再送他去兽医那儿\Nwe'll drop him off at the vet on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.77,0:59:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 耽搁两小时对他算得了什么? - 马蒂 我都约好车了 伙计\N- What's a couple of hours to this guy? - Marty, I got rides set up, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.94,0:59:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,唉 摩西\NHuh. Moses.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.79,0:59:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,三号球道 归你了\NLane three. That's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.76,0:59:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 怎么样? - 有什么能帮您的?\N- Hi, how you doing? - Could I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.56,0:59:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,能给我开个球道吗?\NCan I get a lane?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.52,1:00:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大概得等半小时 四十分钟\NProbably gonna be a half hour, 40 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.52,1:00:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没问题 - 你确定能等?\N- That's okay. - You all right with that?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.69,1:00:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 要租鞋吗? - 我待会儿再拿\N- You want shoes? - I'll just grab 'em later.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.37,1:00:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,搞定 结束\NDone. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.37,1:00:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,弱得可怜 给钱\NFucking pathetic. Pay up.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.24,1:00:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,谁想打下一局?\NWho wants next?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.45,1:00:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我能打吗? 嘿! 我能来一局吗?\NCan I play? Hey! Can I play?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.46,1:00:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一块钱一局 - 行吧\N- It's a dollar a game. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.25,1:00:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你叫什么? - 塞思\N- What's your name? - Seth.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.96,1:00:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,来几个对攻热热身吧\NLet's get a warm-up rally going.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.67,1:00:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不 要打就掏钱 否则闭嘴 我不打白工\NNah. Put up or shut up. I don't play for free.
