Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.81,1:06:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好 让我来说 - 快上车!\N- Okay, just let me do the talking. - Get in the car!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.89,1:07:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧是谁! 搞死这王八蛋!\NLook who it is! Let's get this motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.02,1:07:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,几位 晚上好\NGentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.36,1:07:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了? 哥几个还好吧?\NWhat's going on? How are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.44,1:07:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把钱还我们! - 你们在说什么?\N- Give us our money! - What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.24,1:07:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我正给这位哥们加油呢 - 看看这是谁\N- I'm giving this guy some gas. - Look who it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.91,1:07:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,别玩这套!\NDon't pull that shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.07,1:07:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你他妈设局千我们! - 我没千谁\N- You fucking hustled us! - I didn't hustle anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.53,1:07:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我认得你! 你是他妈的马蒂·毛瑟!\NI know who you are! You're fuckin' Marty Mauser!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.83,1:07:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 冷静点! - 我不认识那人!\N- Relax! - I don't know who that is!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.33,1:07:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,罗杰! 住手! 住手!\NRoger! Stop it! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.79,1:07:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,别 别冲动 有话好说\NNo, relax. Relax. Relax. Relax.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.87,1:07:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,滚出这破车!\NOut of the fucking car!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.96,1:07:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,滚出这破车 你这黑鬼!\NGet out of the fucking car, nigger!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.84,1:07:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 凭什么要我... - 滚出来!\N- Why I gotta be-- - Get the fuck out!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.10,1:07:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,操!\NFuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.31,1:07:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 马蒂 快他妈走! - 操你大爷!\N- Marty, let's fucking go! - Fuck yourself!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.10,1:07:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,走 走 走 走 快走\NGo, go, go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.77,1:07:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,沃利 留神! 留神! 电线杆!\NWally, watch out! Watch out! The pole!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.36,1:07:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不! 不!\NNo! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.86,1:07:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,沃利 狗 狗还在那 沃利\NWally, the dog. The dog, Wally.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.69,1:07:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 去他妈的狗! - 我得带着狗!\N- Fuck that dog! - I need the dog!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.74,1:07:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,去他妈的狗\NFuck the dog,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.82,1:07:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也去你的 伙计! 去你的!\N- and fuck you, man! Fuck you, man! - Oh, no. No!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.12,1:07:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会扣我工资的!\NThey'll take this out of my paycheck!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.66,1:08:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我车废了 伙计! 我他妈要丢工作了!\NMy car's fucked up, man! I'm gonna lose my fucking job!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.71,1:08:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的全部! 我还有人要养呢!\NThis is all I got! I got people depending on me!
