Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.99,1:09:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 马蒂\NHey, Marty.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.26,1:09:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 泰德 - 嘿 马蒂 伙计 近来可好?\N- Hey, Ted. - Hey, Marty. How you doing, man?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.97,1:09:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 劳伦斯在吗? - 节哀顺变\N- Is Lawrence here? - Sorry about your loss.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.26,1:09:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 劳伦斯今晚在这儿吗?\NIt's all right. Is Lawrence here tonight?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.93,1:09:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,昂 在 就在这附近哪个地儿\NUh, yeah. He's around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.72,1:09:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 知道了 谢了 - 行 行\N- Okay. All right. Thank you. - Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.64,1:09:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 见到你很高兴 伙计 - 嗯\N- Good to see you, man. - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.35,1:09:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 最近怎么样? - 马蒂\N- How you been? - Marty.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.52,1:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 见到你真好 - 嘿 马蒂\N- Nice to see you. - Hello, Marty.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.40,1:09:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 今晚能借住你的后屋吗 求你了?\NHey, can I stay in your back room tonight, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.07,1:09:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 你的小妞在后头呢 知道吗?\NHey, hey. Got your girl in the back, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.24,1:09:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,她怀孕了 情绪特别糟\NShe pregnant. She real upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.99,1:09:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 天哪 好吧 知道了\NOh, God. Okay. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.99,1:10:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,额 我去跟她谈谈\NUh, let me go talk to her,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.49,1:10:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但在见我之前 麻烦千万别走开\Nbut then please don't leave without finding me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.12,1:10:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 放心 我就在这儿 - 好 很高兴见到你\N- Yeah, I'll be here. Okay. - All right. Nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.91,1:10:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 很高兴见到你 - 嗯\N- All right, good to see you. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.72,1:10:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你怎么在这儿?\NHey. What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.02,1:10:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我没想打扰你 我知道你很忙\NI don't mean to bother you. I know you're really busy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.68,1:10:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你脸是怎么搞的? - 我真的没别的地方去了\N- What the hell happened to your face? - I didn't really have anywhere else to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.31,1:10:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让我看看 - 他突然就开始...\N- Let me see. - He just started...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.48,1:10:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他突然就开始对我吼\Nhe just started yelling at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.98,1:10:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他疯了一样 还扯我的衣服\NAnd he was really mad and he was ripping my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.23,1:10:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他把你弄成这样的? - 他真的吓死我了\N- He did this to you? - He was really scaring me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.82,1:10:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不知道还能去哪儿\NI just didn't know where else to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.95,1:10:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你在生我的气吗?\NAre you mad at me?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.30,1:11:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞秋?\NRachel?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.59,1:11:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是瑞秋 是马蒂 开门\NNo, it's not Rachel. It's Marty. Open the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.91,1:12:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 迪昂 怎么样 伙计? 真的很感谢\NHey, Dion. How you doing, man? I really appreciate this.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.70,1:12:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便说下 这是我妹妹瑞秋\NThis is my sister Rachel, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.20,1:12:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞秋 这是我哥们 也是生意伙伴 迪昂\NRachel, this is my buddy, my business partner, Dion.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.37,1:12:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 - 嘿\N- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.62,1:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,她那儿淹水了\NHer place flooded.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.96,1:12:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,她得在这儿凑合一晚 没问题吧?\NShe needs a place to crash for the night. That's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.17,1:12:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定 伙计 这...\NI don't know, man, it's...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.25,1:12:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 但我不能让她待在有霉菌孢子什么的破地儿\NI know, but I can't have her exposed to mold and spores and shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.26,1:12:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,迪 拜托 她都怀孕八个月了 懂吗?\ND, come on, she's eight months pregnant, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.47,1:12:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托...\NCome on...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.72,1:12:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是我亲外甥\NThat's my nephew.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.14,1:12:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不该带人回来的\NI'm not supposed to have people over.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.76,1:12:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她家里情况很糟 我不能让她回去 求你了\NShe's got a bad situation at home. I can't have her going back there. Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.14,1:12:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,行吧 进来吧 你可以住一晚\NAll right. Come on. You can spend the night.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.73,1:12:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但明天我爸妈回来前你得离开\NYou just gotta be out of here by tomorrow before my parents get back.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.19,1:12:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题\NOkay. No problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.27,1:12:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们得趁聚在一起把时间利用好\NWe should take advantage of the time we have together.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.03,1:12:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好好敲定咱们的业务计划\NYou know, really firm up our business plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.53,1:12:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这样你爸回来就能看到咱们有多专业了\NThat way, when your dad gets back, he sees how organized we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.86,1:12:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 他现在挺火大的\NYeah, he's pretty upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.20,1:12:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你把这堆库存丢给咱们八个月没管\NYou left us with all of this inventory for eight months.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.95,1:12:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 几周后我拿下冠军\NThat's fine. In a few weeks I'll take the championship.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.99,1:12:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们就能重回正轨\NWe'll be right back on track.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.08,1:12:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 球就在这儿 - 真的? 哪呢?\N- Balls are right in here. - Really? Where?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.83,1:12:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,最上面的箱子\NThe top box.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.50,1:12:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.63,1:13:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哇 你做了橙色的?\N- Whoa. You did the orange? - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.01,1:13:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么做成橙色的?\NHow'd you do the orange?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.09,1:13:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我联系了海力士的人\NI contacted someone at Halex.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.68,1:13:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他们帮我给赛璐珞上了色\NThey colored the celluloid for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.22,1:13:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么搞定的? - 靠钱呗 宝贝\N- How? - Money, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.72,1:13:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我和我老爸都看好你\NMe and my pop, we believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.39,1:13:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们投了钱的 这就是他一直火大的原因\NWe're invested. That's why he's been so mad.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.98,1:13:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这个 瑞秋\NCheck it out, Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.65,1:13:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,来 看看这包装\NHere, check out the packaging.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.73,1:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"马蒂至尊 马蒂·毛瑟锦标赛官方乒乓球\N"Marty Supreme. The official Marty Mauser championship table tennis ball.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.44,1:13:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,专业制造 橙色..."\NProfessionally made. Orange..."
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.69,1:13:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,橙色球体? 你想出来的?\NOrange spheres? You came up with that?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.57,1:13:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 挺棒的吧?\NYeah. Pretty good, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.70,1:13:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,何止棒啊 迪昂 这... 我惊呆了\NPretty good? Dion, this is... I'm stunned.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.95,1:13:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,太震撼了\NI'm stunned.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.08,1:13:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还是手绘的 - 你画的?\N- Hand-drawn too. - You drew this?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.04,1:13:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对 - 真是神来之笔\N- Yeah. - It's inspired.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.46,1:13:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢夸奖\NI appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.54,1:13:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你都不知道自己多有能耐\NI don't think you know what you're capable of.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.46,1:13:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你看 - 真的多谢\N- Check it out. - Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.84,1:13:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哇\NWow.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.09,1:13:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很漂亮\Nit's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.67,1:13:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是你的房间? - 不是 是我弟弟的\N- This is your room? - No, it's my brother's.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.59,1:13:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有弟弟? 你从来没跟我说过\NYou have a brother? You never told me you had a brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.13,1:13:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是个亲弟弟 已经搬走了\NIt's a younger brother. He moved out.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.80,1:13:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那他房间空着?\NSo his room is free?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.22,1:13:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 额 对 - 我先去安顿一下我妹\N- Uh, yeah. - Let me get my sister situated.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.68,1:13:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 五分钟后去找你 - 行\N- I'll come find you in five minutes. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.14,1:13:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,五分钟\NFive minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.39,1:13:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,迪昂 你真让我刮目相看\NI'm really impressed, D.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.89,1:13:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢 - 说真的\N- Thank you. - Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.23,1:13:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个特别的人\NSpecial guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.52,1:14:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我把床给你弄舒服点 好吗?\NLet me get the bed comfortable for you, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.99,1:14:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那你现在要出去吗?\NSo are you gonna go out there now?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.28,1:14:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我得琢磨下明天的计划\NYeah, I gotta figure my plan out for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.36,1:14:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么? 什么计划?\NWhy? Plan for what?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.61,1:14:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我得理理头绪\NWell, I need to get my head together.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.62,1:14:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说?\NHow so?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.12,1:14:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有个有钱佬找我干活 我打算联系他\NThis rich guy hit me up for a job. I think I'm gonna get in touch with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.87,1:14:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的? - 是啊\N- Really? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.04,1:14:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 干什么活? 什么工作? - 不重要 能去日本就行\N- A job for what? What job? - It doesn't matter. Just to get to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.13,1:14:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为了锦标赛? - 对\N- For the championship? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.17,1:14:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,哇\NWow.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.92,1:14:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然生活一团糟 但我会搞定的\NEverything in my life is falling apart, but I'm gonna figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.09,1:14:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,需要帮忙吗? 我可以帮你\NDo you need any help? I could help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.89,1:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没事 不用了 - 我能做点什么吗?\N- No, it's all right. It's all right. - Can I do anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.81,1:14:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你饿吗?\NAre you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.10,1:14:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不饿 - 确定?\N- No. - You sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.81,1:14:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,额 我去另一个房间待着 行吗?\NUh, I'll just be in the other room, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.40,1:14:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 迪昂 我从没见过这种球 - 我就说吧 伙计\N- Dion, I've never seen anything like this. - I told you, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.86,1:14:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计 咱们得好好叙叙旧\NMan, we have to have a big catch-up
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.32,1:14:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这是八个月来发生在我身上最伟大的事\N'cause this is the greatest thing that's happened to me in the last eight months.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.32,1:14:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,谁能想到呢? 海力士?\NWho would've thought? Halex?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.46,1:15:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 洛克威尔油墨公司\NGood morning. Rockwell Ink.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.30,1:15:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 你好 请帮我接米尔顿·洛克威尔先生\NYes, hi, can I speak to Milton Rockwell, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.76,1:15:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在不在 需要留个言吗?\NHe's not in at the moment. Can I take a message?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.84,1:15:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 什么时候能联系到他?\NOkay, when are you expecting him?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.13,1:15:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,额 他今天在外面办公\NWell, he's working off-site today.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.09,1:15:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再问一遍 需要留言吗? - 趁热喝\N- Again, can I take a message?- It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.93,1:15:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,太感谢了\NThank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.26,1:15:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,等我妹醒了 能给她也弄点吗?\NCan you make some for my sister for when she wakes up?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.18,1:15:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她会很饿的 - 喂?\N- She'll be really hungry. - Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.77,1:15:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你说他在外面哪儿?\NYou said off-site where?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.19,1:15:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我不能告诉你相关信息\NI'm sorry, I can't give you that information.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.02,1:15:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 您到底要不要留言? - 要\N- Would you like to leave a message or not?- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.94,1:15:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,能替我向他道个歉吗?\NCan you apologize to him on my behalf?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.44,1:15:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我是原本今早要和他\NI was the young gentleman that was supposed to have breakfast
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.44,1:15:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一起吃早餐的那个年轻人\Nwith him this morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.53,1:15:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不清楚 - 就是他儿子那个营的\N- I'm not familiar.- From his son's battalion.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.91,1:15:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我对此一无所知\NI'm sorry, I-- I don't know anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.78,1:15:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我这儿有他儿子的个人遗物 应该交给他\NI have some personal belongings of his son's I was supposed to give to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.70,1:15:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,信件 纪念品之类的 但我搞砸了 睡过头了\NLetters and mementos and such, but I messed up and I overslept.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.79,1:15:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天就要离开这儿 要不邮寄给他更方便?\NI'm leaving town today, but I could mail it to him if that's easier.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.75,1:15:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 不行 - 不行? 好的\N- No, no, no.- No? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.84,1:15:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吧 你试试往莫罗斯科剧院打个电话\NHow about this, why don't you try giving a call over to the Morosco Theatre.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.51,1:15:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,莫罗斯科剧院\NThe Morosco Theatre.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.88,1:15:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我算什么? 我在干嘛?\NSo, I'm like what? What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.47,1:15:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,跑这儿来毁了我的夜晚\NComing up here to wreck my night.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.89,1:15:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,说真的 妈 我压根不知道你会来\NHonest, Mama, I didn't even know you were coming here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.77,1:15:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我受够了你耍花招\NI'm through with you playing games.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.02,1:15:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是来找点乐子\NI was just coming for a good time.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.27,1:16:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说应召女郎都在这儿扎堆\NI heard this was where all the call girls gather.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.77,1:16:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我正努力重建生活 你不明白吗?\NI'm trying to rebuild my life here. Don't you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.57,1:16:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我看是把自己卖给出价最高的人吧\NMore like selling out to the highest bidder.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.82,1:16:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你没资格评判我 杰德\NYou've got no right to judge me, Jed.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.36,1:16:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我拼尽全力才换来那么一点幸福\NI fought tooth and nail for every shred of happiness
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.58,1:16:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哪怕只有一点... - 对 那你给过我什么?\N- I've ever found while you... - Right, and what did you give to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.16,1:16:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你从没相信过我 一次都没有!\NYou never believed in me. Not once!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.21,1:16:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你想沉溺于自怜吗? 杰德 烤箱在那儿呢!\NYou wanna wallow in self-pity? Well, here's an oven, Jed!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.54,1:16:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔玛!\NAlma!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.63,1:16:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事 亨利\NI'm all right, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.71,1:16:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 请给我们留点私人时间 - 我妈就是个烂货\N- Just give us a minute, please. - My mama is a dirty bird.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.05,1:16:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴放干净点 杰迪代亚\NBe careful now, Jedidiah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.01,1:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你给她穿的那身华丽衣裳 只是掩盖她身上的臭味!\NAnd that fancy dress you put her in is the only thing keeping in the stench!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.60,1:16:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不许碰我孩子\NDon't you lay a hand on my child.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.85,1:16:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我... 抱歉 额...\NI-I'm sorry, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.27,1:16:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,妈 我做错什么了?\NMama, what did I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.73,1:16:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,走! 快跑!\NGo! Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.12,1:16:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 门锁了 - 噢 我的天\N- The door is locked. - Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.79,1:17:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑!\NYou've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.16,1:17:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼 谁给这门加了插销?\NFor Christ's sake, did somebody put a latch on the door?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.46,1:17:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢天呐 - 我以为刚才节奏挺好的\N- Oh, God. - I thought we had a good rhythm going.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.96,1:17:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,节奏挺好? 你住哪个星球啊 节奏算哪门子好\NA good rhythm going? On what planet is that a good rhythm
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.25,1:17:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果你就自个儿在那演? - 我入戏了\N- if you're alone in a room? - I was in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.67,1:17:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,搞得跟我不在场一样 入戏? 戏在哪呢?\NIt's like I wasn't even there. In it? In what?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.34,1:17:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 格伦 我一句话都插不上 - 我懂 咱们会修正的\N- Glenn, I couldn't get a word out. - I understand. We're gonna fix it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.26,1:17:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 排练过程就是为了解决这些 - 真他妈绝了\N- That's what a rehearsal process is for. - Fuck's sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.76,1:17:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,先停一下吧 大家休息五分钟\NLet's lose this, by the way. Everybody take five.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.85,1:17:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,帮个忙 各位...\NDo me a favor, everybody...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.27,1:17:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,得有人跟他说说这事\NSomebody needs to tell him something.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.56,1:17:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 简直离谱 - 不可理喻\N- It's impossible. - Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.90,1:17:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 喝水吗? - 喝\N- Do you want some water? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.69,1:17:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我去给你拿点 - 天哪\N- Let me bring you some. - God.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.78,1:17:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 凯\NHey, Kay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.28,1:17:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 是马蒂\NHey, it's Marty.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.16,1:17:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,伦敦那个\NFrom London.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.46,1:17:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么跑这儿来了?\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.54,1:17:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,额 我有个舞台技师协会的朋友\NWell, I got a friend in the stagehands union.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.29,1:17:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我过来给他送点东西\NI was dropping something off for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.54,1:17:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你刚才看了? - 是的 希望没冒犯到你\N- You watched that? - Yeah, I hope that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.71,1:17:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 天呐\NOh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.84,1:17:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 没想到你又开始演戏了\NHey, I can't believe you're acting again.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.17,1:17:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那不叫演戏 他压根不让我演\NThat wasn't acting. He won't let me act.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.34,1:17:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 看得出来挺闹心的 那家伙什么来头?\NYeah, no, that looked frustrating. What's the deal with that guy?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.01,1:18:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,别提了\NDon't get me started.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.35,1:18:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 你刚才演技完全吊打他\NYeah, you were running circles around him.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.85,1:18:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那是当然\NOf course I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.06,1:18:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,确实 简直神了\NYeah. It was unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.69,1:18:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他连续三天不睡觉\NHe stays up for three days in a row
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.35,1:18:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为他的角色应该很疲惫\Nbecause his character is supposed to be tired.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.69,1:18:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 简直不可理喻 - 噢天呐\N- It's obnoxious. - Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.78,1:18:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要是他真那么投入 为什么要停下来?\NIf he's so committed, why'd he stop the scene?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.07,1:18:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他干嘛不一拳打穿那个帘子\NWhy didn't he punch his hand through the screen,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.95,1:18:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,从里面把锁打开?\Nunlock it from the other side?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.62,1:18:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对吧? 换我会这么干 - 格伦!\N- Right? That's what I would've done. - Glenn!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.41,1:18:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来了 - 格伦!\N- Yeah. - Glenn!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.58,1:18:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 来了 - 我有话跟你说\N- Yes. Thank you. Yes. - I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.13,1:18:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了? - 什么?\N- Yes, what? - What? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.42,1:18:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这小子比他更懂这个角色\NThis kid understands the character better than he does.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.80,1:18:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么?\NExcuse me?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.09,1:18:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把你刚才跟我说的话告诉他 - 不 我不想说\N- Tell him what you just told me. - No, I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.68,1:18:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,说吧 告诉他\NNo, tell him.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.76,1:18:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是觉得你刚才看起来没入戏 仅此而已\NI was just saying you didn't really seem like you were in the scene is all.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.22,1:18:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 额 这位是谁? - 他谁也不是 关键就在这儿\N- Uh, who is this? - He's nobody. That's the point.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.64,1:18:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 以我的经验 只有小孩才会那样拿刀\NAlso, you know, in my experience, only children hold a knife like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.57,1:18:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,要是真打 刀应该这么拿\NIf it's a serious fight, you hold your knife like this,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.19,1:18:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 刀刃要垂直于手腕 - 这又不是街头斗殴\N- with the blade square to your wrist. - This is not a street fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.15,1:18:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 如果你不追求真实感的话\NOkay, well, if you're not going for realistic,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.74,1:18:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那你还得再加点花样\Nyou might as well add a little flair.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.58,1:19:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就像这样\NLike that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.74,1:19:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别闹了 - 对吧 凯?\N- Cut it out. - Right, Kay?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.08,1:19:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 行了 谢了您的教程 非常感谢\NOkay. Yeah, okay. Thanks for the tutorial. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.08,1:19:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太感谢了 今天就到这吧 谢谢\NThank you very much indeed. That's all we need today. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.83,1:19:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 祝你好运 凯 万事顺利 - 让他滚出去!\N- Best of luck, Kay. Best of luck. - Get him out!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.59,1:19:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这里不需要你了 非常感谢\NWe no longer require your presence. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.63,1:19:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我直言...\NWell, with all due respect...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.01,1:19:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,可每套布景都要花掉五千多块\NAnd yet every set cost more than $5,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.09,1:19:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我没法打个响指 就把你老婆和钱都搞顺当\NI can't just snap my fingers and get your money and your wife into alignment.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.35,1:19:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我付你钱是让你想办法的\NI pay you to say no.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.97,1:19:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,她似乎觉得这是在拿空头支票开玩笑\NShe seems to think that this is carte blanche.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.68,1:19:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我没法在这里完成不可能的任务\NI can't just perform the impossible here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.77,1:19:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你管不住她 我就找个能管住的人来\NIf you can't control her, I will find someone else who can.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.15,1:19:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋\NAsshole.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.07,1:19:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,洛克威尔先生 洛克威尔先生\NMr. Rockwell. Mr. Rockwell.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.07,1:19:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 干什么? - 嘿 马蒂·毛瑟 见到你真好\N- What? - Hey. Marty Mauser. Nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.70,1:19:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是你往我办公室打电话 说是跟我儿子是哥们的?\NDid you call my office and say you're friends with my son?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.58,1:19:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 但是... - 该死!\N- Yes. But... - Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.96,1:19:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我没别的办法联系你了 拜托\NI had no other way to get in touch with you. Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.04,1:19:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我想重新谈谈去日本的事\NI wanna revisit our conversation about Japan.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.67,1:19:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我重新考虑过了 我想去 我觉得那是绝佳的主意\NI reconsidered it and I wanna do it. I think it's a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.92,1:19:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,比赛就在下周 我已经有别的打算了\NThe event's next week. I've made alternate plans.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.84,1:19:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,什么打算? 嘿 那可是你的主意\NWhat other plans? Okay, it was your idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.55,1:20:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这主意棒极了 咱们就花两秒钟谈谈这事吧\NIt's a fantastic idea. Let's just have a conversation about this for two seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.59,1:20:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你干什么呢? 嘿 嘿 洛克威尔先生\NWhat are you doing? Hey. Hey. Mr. Rockwell.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.18,1:20:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 咱们都现实一点好吗\NPlease, let's both be pragmatists about this.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.10,1:20:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,把你对我的个人成见先放一边\NPut your personal feelings about me aside for a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.27,1:20:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你我都很清楚 我和远藤古都打能创造多大价值\NYou and I both know how much value I would add with Endo.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.35,1:20:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在他的主场打表演赛?\NIn an exhibition on his home turf?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.23,1:20:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,想象一下 我就像根炸药引信\NImagine it. I'd be like a stick of dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.15,1:20:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你现在的备选方案是什么\NWhatever you have planned, the alternative,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.73,1:20:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,跟这个比起来都黯然失色\Nit's gonna pale in comparison.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.11,1:20:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,请给我两分钟时间\NPlease give me two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.32,1:20:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们有很多共识能解决这问题 拜托!\NWe have enough common ground to figure this out. Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.49,1:20:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 行吧 上车说 - 真的? 谢谢\N- All right, get in the car. - Really? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.95,1:20:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,汤米 开车\NTommy, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.95,1:20:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 嘿! 嘿! - 嘿!\N- Hey. Hey! Hey! - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.33,1:20:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你个狗娘养的 那个主意还是我给你的!\NYou son of a bitch. I gave you the idea!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.18,1:20:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 斯通小姐让我转告你\NI'm sorry. Miss Stone wanted to let you know
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.89,1:20:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她很乐意和你共进午餐\Nthat she'd love to have lunch with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.72,1:20:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 斯通小姐? - 是的\N- Miss Stone? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.07,1:21:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 我迟到太久了\NMy God, I'm so late.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.58,1:21:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 你管那么多干嘛?\NCome on. What do you care?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.16,1:21:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你可是主角 这感觉应该很爽吧?\NYou're the star. Gotta feel pretty good, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.71,1:21:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 你当初为什么要息影?\NI mean, why'd you even stop in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.58,1:21:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要稳定 后来我怀孕了\NI wanted security, and I got pregnant,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.09,1:21:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,加上他的压力 我就妥协了\Nand he pressured me, and I settled.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.88,1:21:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 显然你现在做的是正确决定\NWell, I mean, clearly, you're doing the right thing now
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.30,1:21:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而且听起来他正加倍补偿你呢\Nand it sounds like he's paying you back with interest.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.47,1:21:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁? - 你丈夫\N- Who is? - Your husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.64,1:21:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 你的整场演出都是他出钱吧?\NI mean, he's funding your whole show, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.22,1:21:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你哪来的这种想法?\NWhere'd you get that idea?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.31,1:21:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我在大堂无意中听到他在抱怨\NI overheard him complaining about it in the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.97,1:21:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 抱怨? - 是的 抱怨开销太大\N- Complaining? - Yeah, about the costs.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.98,1:21:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,让他滚一边去吧\NHe can go fuck himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.52,1:21:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 彻底滚蛋 你知道你该怎么做\NCompletely. You know what you should do,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.15,1:21:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该榨干他的每一分钱\Nyou should leech him for every penny he's worth,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.07,1:21:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,坐稳你全球头号巨星的位子\Nassume your place as the biggest star on the planet,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.86,1:21:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,然后狠狠打他那张自大嘴脸\Nand then you rub it in his smug little face.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.74,1:21:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 但我真的不需要你来教我做事\NThank you, but I'm really not looking for life advice from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.86,1:21:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我只是说你打从一开始就不需要他\NNo, I'm just saying you clearly never needed him in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.41,1:21:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我 我从不接受任何人的帮助\NLike with me, I'm never accepting anyone's help.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.58,1:21:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我得完全靠自己 纯粹靠我自己的天赋\NI gotta do it completely on my own. Purely on the basis of my own talent.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.71,1:21:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,否则的话 这种成功就不算数了\NOtherwise it's, like, the success won't even count.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.88,1:22:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这只是我个人的想法\NBut that's just me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.09,1:22:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 这种话听起来倒是容易\NYes, well, that's very easy to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.38,1:22:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来容易 做起来可真难\NWell, it's easy to say but it's sure not easy to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.26,1:22:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 你懂的 所以你才拿钱退出了\NI mean, you know that. That's why you cashed out.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.01,1:22:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我问你个事\NLet me ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.02,1:22:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你搞这种乒乓球的小玩意儿能挣钱吗?\NDo you make money at this little table tennis thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.48,1:22:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还没呢 - 你有工作吗?\N- Not yet. - Do you have a job?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.31,1:22:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 我是说 乒乓球就是我的工作\NNo. I mean, table tennis is my job.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.48,1:22:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那你靠什么生活?\NHow do you live?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.57,1:22:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我靠信念活着\NI live with the confidence
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.65,1:22:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我相信自己 钱自然会来的\Nthat if I believe in myself, the money will follow.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.44,1:22:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,归根结底 我的奋斗不全是为了钱\NUltimately, my struggle isn't even about money.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.99,1:22:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你怎么交房租? - 我不交\N- How do you pay rent? - I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.16,1:22:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在回避问题 - 不 我没回避任何事\N- You're avoiding the question. - No, I'm not avoiding anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.33,1:22:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那你今天打算怎么解决吃饭问题?\NHow do you plan on eating food today?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.12,1:22:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话 打算等你一走我就叫客房服务\NHonestly, I was gonna order room service the second you leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.54,1:22:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 漂亮 - 确实 漂亮\N- Nice. - Yeah. Nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.04,1:22:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你这整套梦想最终没成 你打算怎么办?\NAnd what do you plan to do if this whole dream of yours doesn't work out?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.21,1:22:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我压根就没考虑过这种可能\NThat doesn't even enter my consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.38,1:22:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,行吧 也许你应该考虑下\NOkay. Well, maybe it should.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.18,1:22:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哇\NWow.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.72,1:22:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你听起来像我妈 无意冒犯\NYou sound like my mom. No offense.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.51,1:22:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你听起来像个小屁孩\NAnd you sound like a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.35,1:22:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 是吗? 显然我年纪够大了\NOh, yeah? Clearly I'm old enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.60,1:22:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思?\NAnd what is that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.98,1:22:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,意思就是我年纪够大 可以在你复出的节骨眼\NThat I'm old enough to fuck you in your hotel room
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.65,1:23:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在你酒店房间里把你办了\Nin the middle of your big comeback.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.52,1:23:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你真恶心\NYou're disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.03,1:23:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,祝演出顺利\NBreak a leg.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.78,1:23:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我知道 但我当时出城了\NNo, I know, but I was out of town
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.58,1:23:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我昨天才刚收到那份东西\Nso I only just received it yesterday for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.46,1:23:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 不去日本是不可能的\NWell, look, not coming to Japan is not an option.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.92,1:23:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 请转告赛斯先生 全额的银行本票\NOkay, well, just let Mr. Sethi know that a cashier's check in the full amount
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.13,1:23:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,已经在路上了 已经寄出了\Nis already on the way to him. It's in the mail.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.59,1:23:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没关系的 但只是...\NNo, that's fine, but just...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.72,1:23:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望有人对我到场有误会\NI don't want any confusion about my attendance.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.72,1:23:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我会准时出席 比赛开始我就在那儿\NI'm gonna be there. I'm gonna be there when the tournament starts.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.76,1:23:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拿到了! - 耶! 太棒了!\N- I got it! - Yes! Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.10,1:23:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得值多少?\NHow much do you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.64,1:23:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这东西是假的 - 你说什么叫是假的?\N- This is not real. - What do you mean it's not real?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.27,1:23:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 彻头彻尾的假货 - 这可是从千万富婆脖子上摘下来的\N- Total fake. - It came from the neck of a millionaire.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.48,1:23:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我亲眼看着从她脖子上摘下的\NI saw it come off her neck.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.90,1:23:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管哪来的 这就是垃圾\NI don't care where it came from. It's total garbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.95,1:23:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 廉价首饰 - 廉价首饰?\N- Costume jewelry. - Costume jewelry?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.86,1:23:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 操\NOh, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.32,1:23:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要的话 我可以出两块钱收了\NIf you want, I can give you two bucks for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.03,1:23:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 喂? - 嘿 迪昂 是我\N- Hello.- Hey, Dion. It's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.25,1:23:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么样?\NHow are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.33,1:24:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你跑哪去了? 你答应过要弄到经销商名单的\NHey, where have you been? You promised me we'd have a list of distributors.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.29,1:24:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸今晚就落地了\NMy dad lands tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.42,1:24:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我这就回去 全力配合你\NI'll come back now and give you my undivided attention.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.17,1:24:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,先让我跟我妹说两句\NLet me just talk to my sister for a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.80,1:24:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞秋 马蒂来电话了\NRachel, Marty's on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.63,1:24:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 你在哪呢? - 嗨 瑞秋 听着\N- Hi. Where are you?- Hi, Rachel, listen.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.38,1:24:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我夹克里有个狗项圈 明白吗?\NThere's a dog collar in my jacket, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.72,1:24:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识个在新泽西丢了狗的家伙\NI know a guy who lost a dog out in New Jersey.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.64,1:24:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他会付大笔赏金\NHe'll pay a big reward.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.22,1:24:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 正门口碗里有一串车钥匙\NAlso, there's a set of car keys in a bowl by the front door.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.98,1:24:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 见着了吗? - 见到了\N- You see them?- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.14,1:24:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,把钥匙拿上 别让迪昂瞧见\NGrab the keys, and make sure Dion doesn't see you do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.94,1:24:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 迪昂\NHey, Dion.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.02,1:24:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,能去商店帮我买点生姜吗?\NCan you go to the store and grab me some ginger?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.02,1:24:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我晨吐反应特别厉害\NI'm having really bad morning sickness.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.44,1:24:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\NHi.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.41,1:24:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 油站关门了\NSorry, station's closed.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.95,1:24:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 我们不是来加油的\NThat's okay. We're not looking for service.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.20,1:24:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你看见这附近有狗出没吗?\NDid you see a dog come around here?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.12,1:24:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没 啥也没见着 你瞧见狗了吗?\NNah, I ain't seen nothing. You seen a dog?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.21,1:24:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 差不多这么高 - 什么时候丢的?\N- He's this tall. - When did you lose it?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.08,1:24:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,几天前\NA few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.38,1:24:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,克兰伯里有个收容所 往那走大概五英里\NThere's a pound down in Cranberry. About five miles that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.92,1:24:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也许去那试试 - 我打过电话了\N- Maybe try there. - I called there.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.88,1:24:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉 帮不上忙 - 好吧\N- Sorry, can't help you. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.47,1:24:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.40,1:25:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他们什么也没瞧见\NThey didn't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.03,1:25:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们去那儿试试\NLet's go try that place.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.86,1:25:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.78,1:25:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗?\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.91,1:25:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你去哪? - 我去后面瞧瞧\N- Where are you going? - Just gonna check out back.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.00,1:26:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 操 摩西\NOh, shit. Moses.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.96,1:26:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们非常感谢全国各地的唱片商和艺术家们\NWe're grateful to the record manufacturers and artists
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.38,1:26:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,全国各地的艺术家们\Nall over the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.72,1:26:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 伙计 嘿 嘿 摩西\NHey, buddy. Hey. Hey, Moses.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.48,1:26:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是我 马蒂 嘿 伙计 噢 操\NIt's Marty. Hey, buddy. Oh, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.15,1:26:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 伙计\NHey, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.86,1:26:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,摩西 摩西!\NMoses. Moses!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.94,1:26:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 伙计 冷静点 咱们带你回家\NHey, buddy. Calm down. Let's get you home.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.32,1:26:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你想回家的 对吧? 咱们回家\NYou wanna go home, right? Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.20,1:26:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 嘿 别别别别别\NOkay. Hey. No, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.28,1:26:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才为您播放的是佩珀敏特·哈里斯\NAnd that was Peppermint Harris
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.16,1:26:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,以及他的那首金曲...\Nand that great record of his...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.54,1:26:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不过现在是时候暂别这档节目了\NBut it's time to hang up the old blunderbuss for now.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.13,1:26:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,记住 如果你想...\NRemember, if you want any...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.93,1:27:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 你好? - 有什么事?\N- Hi, how are you? - Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.26,1:27:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正帮附近丢了狗的人找狗\NWe were just searching the area for a lost dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.93,1:27:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- "我们"? - 我和我丈夫\N- "We"? - My husband and I.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.64,1:27:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的狗几天前在加油站附近丢了\NWe lost our dog a couple of days ago out near the gas station
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.02,1:27:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他们叫我们来这边瞧瞧...\Nand they told us to come and check over here...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.52,1:27:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 既然你是最近的一户人家 - 谁?\N- seeing that you're the closest house. - Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.15,1:27:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,谁? 哪个加油站?\NWho? Which gas station?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.28,1:27:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不知道 - 嘿!\N- I don't know. - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.44,1:27:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是那里一个工作的伙计说的\NIt was one of the guys that work there.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.61,1:27:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢 伙计 看到你回来真激动 - 他就在那儿!\N- Oh, man, I'm so excited you're back. - There he is!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.49,1:27:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我觉得你可能找到了我们的狗 - 你们在私闯民宅\N- I think you might've found our dog. - You're trespassing.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.28,1:27:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不 抱歉 我们没那意思 我们听到后院有狗叫\NNo. I'm sorry, that's not our intention. We heard barking in the back.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.12,1:27:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我压根不知道你在说什么\NI have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.79,1:27:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我的狗 你找到了\NMy dog. You found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.62,1:27:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我没找着什么狗\NI didn't find any dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.21,1:27:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定?\NAre you sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.38,1:27:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,废话 我确定 你确定?\NYeah, I'm sure. Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.00,1:27:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊...\NYeah...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.51,1:27:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我看了你的窗户\NI looked through your window.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.59,1:27:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我看到我的狗了 - 你居然窥探我的窗户?\N- I saw my dog. - You were looking through my window?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.22,1:27:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,幸亏我看了 不是吗?\NIt was a good thing I did, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.38,1:27:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,在我叫警察之前 赶紧从我的地盘滚出去\NGet the hell off my property before I call the police.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.30,1:27:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,该叫警察的是我\NI should call the police.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.72,1:27:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,行啊 你想近距离看看他吗?\NOkay. You wanna get a closer look at him?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.97,1:27:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想近距离看看? - 是的 求你了\N- You wanna closer look? - Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.35,1:27:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 行 挺好 - 我就让你看个够\N- Okay, good, good. - I'll give you a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.07,1:27:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿!\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.82,1:28:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静点\NCalm down.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.45,1:28:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我很冷静\NI am calm.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.37,1:28:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 要是再让我看到你这张犹太脸... - 你认真的?\N- If I see your kike face... - Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.45,1:28:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- ...再敢窥探我的窗户 - 马蒂 快上车!\N- ...looking through my window again... - Marty, get in the car!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.21,1:28:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗?\NAre you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.46,1:28:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...我就开枪把它崩了\N...I'm gonna shoot it off.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.71,1:28:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没必要那样 我们这就走 马蒂 快上车!\NThere's no need for that. We're leaving. Marty, get in!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.29,1:28:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么?\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.26,1:29:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 钱太多了 太多了 - 不 直接说 他他妈有的是钱\N- It's too much money. It's too much. - No, say it. He's fucking loaded.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.93,1:29:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 喂? - 告诉他\N- Hello?- Tell him.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.60,1:29:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想 拿两千块钱还算公道\NI was thinking maybe $2,000 seems fair for this kind of a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.81,1:29:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得挺公道的\NThat seems pretty fair to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.31,1:29:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 两千 - 你开玩笑呢吧?\N- Two thousand. - You're joking, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.69,1:29:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没开玩笑 - 简直他妈的离谱\N- No, no. No. - That's fucking ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.32,1:30:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 听着...\NLook, look...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.65,1:30:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这事跟你没关系\NI know it's really not your problem,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.61,1:30:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但我快生了 而且 瞧 我现在也没丈夫\Nbut I'm about to have a baby, and, look, I got no husband right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.41,1:30:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我没工作 这笔钱真的 真的能帮到我\NI got no job, and this money would really, really help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.45,1:30:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 你懂的 咱们都是好人...\NAnd, you know, let's be good people and...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.41,1:30:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道那条狗是我从收容所免费领的 对吧?\NYou realize I got that dog for free at the pound, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.42,1:30:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,额 那你这看法可就不对了\NWell, that's kind of the wrong way to look at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.17,1:30:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢 是吗? - 是的 真的\N- Oh, really?- Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.42,1:30:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那我该怎么看?\NHow am I supposed to look at it?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.92,1:30:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们就这么说吧 我现在打这电话不是为了狗\N'Cause let's just say that I'm not calling about a dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.72,1:30:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,假设我这电话是为你妈打的\NLet's say that I'm calling about your mother,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.39,1:30:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个医生 我得给她做急诊手术\Nand I'm a doctor, and I gotta perform emergency surgery on her
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.39,1:30:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,否则她就没命了 你会怎么做?\Nor she's gonna die. What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.06,1:30:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为你妈也是"免费"来的 你就拒绝手术?\NRefuse the surgery because you got your mother for free?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.60,1:30:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不! 那太疯了 你肯定会同意手术\NNo! That's crazy. You're gonna take the surgery
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.44,1:30:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 因为你爱你妈 - 这是我听过最蠢的话\N- because you love your mother. - That's the stupidest thing I ever heard.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.44,1:30:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那我看你压根不懂什么是爱\NWell, then I guess you don't know anything about love.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.32,1:30:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 别扯了 给我地址 好吗? 我现在就过去\NAll right, forget it. Give me your address, okay? I'll come now.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.86,1:30:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我带现金过去 - 抱歉 但不行\N- I'll bring you the cash.- I'm sorry, but no.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.12,1:30:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不行? - 不行\N- No?- No.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.49,1:30:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这真的不是你的错 听起来你也是个大好人\Nit's really not your fault, and you sound like a very nice person.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.83,1:30:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,只是我以前被坑过太多次了\NIt's just I've been ripped off one too many times in the past,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.37,1:30:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我再也不想让那种事发生了\Nand I'm just not willing to let that happen to me again.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.25,1:31:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 咱们得想个办法 让我先拿到钱\NSo, we're just gonna need to find a way to get me the money first.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.42,1:31:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你懂吗? 对 - 真的吗?\N- You know? Yeah. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.92,1:31:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,给我听好了 你这个他妈的臭娘们\NListen to me, you fucking dumb bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.76,1:31:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你一分钱也别想拿到... - 你有什么毛病?\N- You're not getting one red cent...- What is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.88,1:31:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...除非我亲眼见到它\N...without me laying eyes on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.13,1:31:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果你真的不在乎... - 听明白了吗 妹子?\N- If you really don't give a shit about... - You understand, sister?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.72,1:31:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...你那只白捡的狗 没准我该把它捐给医学界做研究?\N...your dog that you got for free, how about I donate him to medical science?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.39,1:31:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想要那种结果吗? - 我就说这行不通\N- Would that be something you want? - I told you this wasn't gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.23,1:31:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我早该知道的 我在干什么啊?\NI should have known better. What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.98,1:31:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真是个烂主意 - 马蒂!\N- It was a terrible idea. - Marty!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.23,1:31:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 蠢透了 - 抱歉 我当时想...\N- It was moronic. - I'm sorry, I was--
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.65,1:31:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我只是想试一把\NI'm sorry. I was trying to give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.90,1:31:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不是你的错 是这事太蠢了 - 好了 冷静点\N- It's not your fault. It was stupid. - All right. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.57,1:31:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那狗是什么颜色的?\NWhat color is the dog?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.53,1:31:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛? 谁在乎啊 是棕色的\NWhy? Who cares? It's brown.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.87,1:31:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 因为我老板认识当地所有的育犬师\NOkay, because my boss knows all of the local breeders,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.79,1:31:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没准咱们能找只长得一样的\Nand maybe we can get one that looks the same,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.91,1:31:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,主人肯定分不出区别\Nand the owner won't be able to tell the difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.58,1:31:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得他会认不出他心爱的狗?\NYou don't think he's gonna recognize his own dog that he loves?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.50,1:31:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是说起码一开始认不出 - 我现在本该在练球\N- I'm saying maybe not at first. - I should be working on my game right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.75,1:31:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,结果我现在却在二手车场\NInstead, I'm in a used car lot
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.42,1:31:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,玩这种恶作剧电话 把生活搞得像个笑话\Nmaking a mockery of my life, doing prank calls.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.81,1:32:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们在干什么? - 嘿 你怎么还没睡?\N- What are you guys doing? - Hey. What are you still doing up?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.77,1:32:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,小点声 我爸妈在睡觉\NKeep your voice down. My parents are sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.78,1:32:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不知道他们回来了 - 我告诉过你他们回来了\N- I didn't know they were back. - I told you they were back.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.53,1:32:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我爸的车呢? - 在车库里\N- Where's my dad's car? - It's in the garage.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.86,1:32:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,迪昂 我跟你说 我们这一天过得简直难以置信\NYou're not gonna believe, Dion, when I tell you the day that we had.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.95,1:32:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你骗了我 - 不 我没有 你在说什么呢?\N- You tricked me. - No, I didn't. What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.12,1:32:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你确实骗了 你这骗子婊子 - 喔\N- Yes, you did, you lying bitch. - Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.04,1:32:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘴放干净点 你这死肥猪\NHey, you watch your mouth, you fat piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.00,1:32:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别这么跟我说话 - 别这么跟他说话\N- Don't talk to me like that. - Don't talk to him like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.79,1:32:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他可是我全世界最铁的朋友\NHe's one of my favorite people on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.00,1:32:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 叫他别这么跟我说话 - 别这么跟她说话\N- Tell him not to talk to me like that. - Don't talk to her like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.71,1:32:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别这么跟他说话 - 小声点\N- Don't talk to him like that. - Keep it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.04,1:32:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是我让她干的 我不开口她肯定不会干\NI'm the one that told her to do it. She wouldn't have if I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.34,1:32:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把车钥匙给我 - 行 就在这儿 拿着\N- Give me the car keys. - Okay, they're right here. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.05,1:32:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 咱们出了点小剐蹭... - 什么?\N- We got into a little fender bender... - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.64,1:32:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...但没大碍\N...but it's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.72,1:32:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 只是点小伤 我会赔的 - 拿什么赔? 什么时候赔?\N- It's minor damage. I can pay for it. - How? When?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.39,1:32:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,迪昂 这么晚了 咱们都该歇歇了\NDion, it's very late right now. We should all get a little bit of rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.52,1:32:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,明早吃早饭时我会跟你爸解释清楚\NI'll smooth it over with your father at breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.02,1:32:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他不会生气的... - 你们不能住这儿!\N- He's not gonna get angry-- - You're not staying here!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.73,1:32:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 咱们没别的地方住了 - 你们必须得走\N- We got no other place to stay. - You guys gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.02,1:32:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不 迪昂 咱们必须得留下\NNo. Dion. We have to stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.44,1:32:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 咱们没处去... 迪昂 别赶人 - 不行 嘘\N- We have nowhere-- Dion. Stop it. - No. Shh.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.36,1:32:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,她都怀孕八个月了 你疯了吗?\NShe's eight months pregnant. Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.11,1:32:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 咱们能不能再谈谈? - 声音小点\N- Please can we just talk about it? - Keep your voice down.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.82,1:32:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,深更半夜的 你要把咱们赶到大街上?\NGonna throw us out in the street in the dead of night?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.16,1:32:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没错 走吧 - 咱们真的没地方去\N- Yeah, yeah. - We've got nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.87,1:32:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,拿上你们的破烂赶紧滚\NGet your shit and leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.83,1:32:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道咱们今天经历了什么吗?\NDo you have any idea what we've been through today?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.91,1:33:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我没在跟你说话\NI'm not talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.41,1:33:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想跟我说话?\NYou're not talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.25,1:33:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你彻底不打算跟我说话了?\NNow you're not talking to me, period?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.13,1:33:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真离谱\NUnbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.63,1:33:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,含着金汤匙出生肯定很爽吧\NMust be nice being born with a silver spoon in your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.55,1:33:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,而咱们有些人得为了生活奔波\NMeanwhile, some of us have to work for a living.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.55,1:33:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你听过"工作"这词儿吗?\NYou ever heard that word, "work"?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.38,1:33:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是整天躲屋里涂鸦\NInstead of doodling in your room all day?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.26,1:33:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,居然把朋友往大街上赶...\NThrowing your friends out on the street...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.93,1:33:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别一直盯着咱们看行吗? 看墙去\NCan you not stare at us? Can you look at the wall?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.73,1:33:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,看得我毛骨悚然\NYou're creeping me out.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.22,1:33:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们要去哪? 因为...\NWhere are we gonna go? Because...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.98,1:33:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对不住 既然这儿就有张床... - 没事的\N- I'm sorry. You have a bed right here... - It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.15,1:33:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- ...我本来能睡上面的 - 没事的\N- ...and I could be sleeping on it. - It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.03,1:33:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我肚里还有个娃呢 我肚里还有个娃呢\NAnd I got a baby in me. I got a baby in me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.28,1:33:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你在干嘛?\NSee what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.36,1:33:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,大半夜的把孕妇赶出门\NYou're throwing a pregnant woman out in the dead of the night.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.82,1:33:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你会一辈子受良心谴责的\NIt's gonna live on your conscience forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.95,1:33:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你干嘛要这么折磨自己? - 对不起\N- Why would you do this to yourself? - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.91,1:33:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,能让我陪她待一会儿吗? 我得安慰她\NCan I have a moment with her, please? Just to comfort her,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.54,1:33:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我亲妹妹单独待会 好吗?\Nin privacy with my sister, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.12,1:33:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让她小声点 - 我尽量 但我得先让她冷静下来\N- Keep her voice down. - I'm gonna try, but I gotta calm her down.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.50,1:33:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.25,1:33:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么办 我不知道该怎么办\NI don't know what to do. I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.51,1:33:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,演得真好\NThat was really good.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.93,1:33:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 瑞秋 演得太牛了 - 谢谢\N- That was amazing, Rachel. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.55,1:33:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,太到位了 没准能成\NThat was so good, it might work.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.76,1:33:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果他把咱们赶走 咱们去哪? - 他现在可能真会留咱们住下\N- Where are we gonna go if he kicks us out? - He might actually let us stay now.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.97,1:33:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那演技简直绝了\NThat acting was so brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.77,1:34:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你真的在哭吗? - 没 马蒂 你在干什么?\N- Are you actually crying? - No. Marty, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.35,1:34:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是什么? - 什么?\N- What is that? - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.65,1:34:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这是化妆品?\NIs this makeup?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.32,1:34:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\NHold on.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.53,1:34:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,等等听我说 听我解释 这不怪我 好吗?\NJust wait. Because I can explain. It's not my fault. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.86,1:34:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\NNo talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.95,1:34:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我也是没法子 你懂吗? - 够了 求你别说了 闭嘴\N- I didn't have a choice, you know? - Stop. Stop, please. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.66,1:34:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 瑞秋 别说了 - 我得离开那儿\N- Rachel, stop. - I needed to get out.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.33,1:34:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 看到我现在有多冷静了吗? 但快到头了 - 对\N- See how calm I am? It's not gonna last. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.54,1:34:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,给我滚出去\NGet the fuck out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.00,1:34:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 我觉得... - 给我滚出去\N- No. What I think-- - Get the fuck out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.67,1:34:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我觉得咱们都该走 因为... - 闭嘴\N- I think that we should both go because... - Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.21,1:34:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这种破事也就我妈能干得出来\NThis is the kinda shit my mother would do to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.84,1:34:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,亏我这么对你 偏偏是你 居然也这么对我?\NHow could you of all people do this to me, the way I treat you?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.13,1:34:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我怎么对你了? - 对 明知道我经历了什么还这么干?\N- How could I do this to you? - Yes, knowing what I'm going through?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.47,1:34:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那你对我做的这些呢? - 够了 嘘 你在干嘛...\N- How about what you're doing to me? - Stop. Shh. What are you doing...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.85,1:34:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕有一秒钟 你考虑过你正在做什么吗...\NHave you ever for one second thought about what you're doing--
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.85,1:34:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 住口 - 闭上你的臭嘴吧 你这自恋的畜生\N- Stop. - Shush yourself, you narcissistic prick.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.81,1:34:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别碰我! - 够了 你们在干什么?\N- Don't touch me! - Stop. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.65,1:34:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你要把我爸妈吵醒了 闭嘴 - 去他妈的你父母吧\N- You're gonna wake my parents up. Shut up. - Enough about your fucking parents.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.06,1:34:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈都三十岁的人了 难道不是吗?\NAren't you, like, 30 years old?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.48,1:34:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你意识到我还有四周就生了吗?\NYou realize I'm due in four weeks?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.32,1:34:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我还有四周就生了! - 孩子又不是我的\N- I am due in four weeks! - It's not my baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.11,1:34:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,而且孩子就是他的 顺便说下 真是他妈的孩子\NAnd it's his baby, by the way. It's his fucking baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.74,1:34:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这事儿他也在撒谎\NHe's lying about that too.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.32,1:35:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我家出什么事了? - 爸 我只是带几个朋友过来\N- What's going on in my house? - I was just having some friends over, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.24,1:35:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计 你还好吗?\NBuddy, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.33,1:35:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 明早咱们得第一时间和斯伯丁开会\NHey, we have a meeting with Spalding first thing in the morning
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.62,1:35:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为了"至尊"的样球 - 迪昂 算了吧 别演了\N- for the Supreme samples. - Dion, come on. Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.58,1:35:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那根本就不可能成\NThat's never gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.21,1:35:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你拿了我儿子的钱 - 您在说什么呢?\N- You've taken my son's money. - What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.50,1:35:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我不信 迪 难道你看不出来发生了什么吗?\NI don't believe it. D, don't you see what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.09,1:35:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 简直离谱 太他妈离谱了... - 你一直都在骗我儿子\N- Unbelievable. Un-fucking... - You're conning my son all along.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.47,1:35:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我才没有骗你儿子 - 你卷走了他所有的钱\N- I am not conning your son. - You're taking all his money.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.26,1:35:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我给了他生活的意义 哪怕你只给了他钱\NI give him meaning. All you do is give him money.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.89,1:35:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我给了他奋斗的目标 - 给我听好!\N- I give him purpose. - You listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.60,1:35:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他他妈看都不敢看你一眼 他怕你怕得要死\NHe won't even fucking look at you, he's so petrified of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.89,1:35:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们怎么办 哈? 你们打算让咱们去哪儿?\NWhat are we gonna do, huh? Where do you expect us to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.81,1:35:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你真想让我睡大街? 我怀孕了\NYou really want me to sleep on the street? I'm pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.06,1:35:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,别 别 迪昂! 迪昂!\NNo, no, no. Dion! Dion!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.38,1:35:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,行吧 瑞秋 我得告诉你件事 我没想针对你\NAll right, I gotta tell you something, Rachel. It's not intended to be mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.43,1:36:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我有我的使命 而你没有\NI have a purpose. You don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.10,1:36:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你觉得那算是什么恩赐 那你就大错特错了\NIf you think that's some sort of blessing, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.60,1:36:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那反倒成了我人生中巨大的劣势\NIt puts me at a huge life disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.85,1:36:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,它意味着我背负着要成就某件事的义务\NIt means I have an obligation to see a very specific thing through.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.35,1:36:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,而那份义务必然伴随着牺牲 懂吗?\NAnd with that obligation comes sacrifice, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.56,1:36:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人生是我所有被迫做出的选择的产物\NMy life is the product of all the choices I've had to make.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.53,1:36:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,而你的人生则是...\NYour life is the product of...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.90,1:36:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道你的人生算什么产物\NI don't even know what your life is the product of.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.49,1:36:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你过一天算一天 你这种人就这样\NYou're making it up as you go. That's the kind of person you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.70,1:36:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不是那种人 懂吗?\NThat's not the kind of person I am, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.91,1:36:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你得为你那些操蛋决定负责\NYou're responsible for the shitty decisions you've made.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.83,1:36:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没叫你结婚 一次都没有\NI never told you to get married, not once.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.87,1:36:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你别想把这些赖在我头上 - 我明白\N- You cannot pawn them off onto me. - I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.58,1:36:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你在宠物店一年挣多少?\NHow much do you make a year at the pet store?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.67,1:36:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多1200块\NAbout $1200.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.75,1:36:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 免得你忘了 我得在一周内弄到1500块\NOkay, in case you forgot, I have a week to make $1500,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.80,1:36:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,还没算机票呢\Nnot including air fare.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.92,1:36:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在得专注 别让我分心\NI need to focus right now, no distractions.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.47,1:36:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的很抱歉 - 没事\N- I'm really sorry. - No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.97,1:36:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,显而易见 我现在没法安定下来\NIt goes without saying, I'm in no position to settle down right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.93,1:36:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,断了这个念头吧 我现在不会安定下来的 好吗?\NGet that out of your mind. I will not settle down right now. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.77,1:36:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你真打算离开艾拉 我不会抛弃你的\NIf you're serious about leaving Ira, I will not abandon you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.19,1:36:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,作为朋友 我会帮你\NAs your friend, I will help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.15,1:36:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们会去查 找个好的待产院\NWe'll do the research, we'll find a great maternity home.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.69,1:36:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会收留你 给孩子找个好人家\NThey'll take you in, they'll ensure the baby's got a good family.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.86,1:36:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以办个... 不行? 怎么了?\NWe could do a-- No? No?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.95,1:37:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那就回家吧 瑞秋 回家去\NThen go home, Rachel. Just go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.53,1:37:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我该怎么说? - 你会想出办法的 回家吧 瑞秋\N- What am I gonna say? - You'll figure it out. Go home, Rachel.
