Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.25,1:44:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 既然座无虚席 目的不就达到了吗?\NWell, I mean, it's a full house. Isn't that the point?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.83,1:44:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,满座的他妈的蠢货 - 不 没那么糟 里面还有点--\NFull of fucking morons. - No, no. You got some--
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.29,1:44:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 弗雷德·阿斯泰尔要来 - 好 我不在这儿碍事了\N- Fred Astaire is coming. - Okay, I'm gonna get out your hair...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.38,1:44:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,别 一定要给他一张今晚的票\NNo. Make sure you give him a ticket for tonight.
