Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.59,1:45:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 小伙子 你这下有福了\NOh. You are in for such a treat, young man.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.97,1:45:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,当你看到这位女士演戏时\NWhen you see this lady act,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.30,1:45:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你会觉得就像被吸尘器口爆了一样\Nyou're gonna feel like you got your cock sucked by a vacuum cleaner.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.27,1:45:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 默尔! - 她脸红了 看见没?\N- Merle! - She's blushing. See her?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.56,1:45:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.56,1:45:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,坐回你那臭位子上\NTake your stinking seat.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.65,1:46:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼?\NWhat the hell?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.20,1:46:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈疯了吗?\NHave you lost your damned mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.12,1:46:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,杰德 我在跟你说话\NJed. I'm talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.25,1:46:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在练准头 妈\NI was just practicing my aim, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.92,1:46:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你总说做人要有大志向\NYou always said to shoot for the stars.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.68,1:46:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.43,1:46:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,过来\NCome.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.06,1:46:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉迟到了 脱不开身\NI'm sorry I'm late. I couldn't get away.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.56,1:46:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 呵 我信 - 他一直缠着我\N- Oh, I bet. - He was all over me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.60,1:46:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你今晚棒极了 简直不可思议\NYou were incredible tonight. That was unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.44,1:46:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我有东西送你 - 给我的?\N- I have something for you. - For me?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.90,1:46:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,转过去\NTurn around.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.32,1:46:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,每年结婚纪念日我丈夫都会送我一件珠宝\NEvery year my husband gives me a piece of jewelry for our anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.28,1:46:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我有25件了 每一件都代表一年的痛苦\NI have 25 of them. One for each year of misery.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.20,1:46:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这够你那趟路费了 没准还有剩\NThat should cover your trip and then some.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.17,1:46:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,戴着这玩意儿让我觉得反胃\NWearing it makes me feel like shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.64,1:47:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 操 停下 停下 停下\NOh, shit. Stop, stop, stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.47,1:47:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,停\NStop.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.35,1:47:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿! 嘿 你们在干什么?\NHey! Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.89,1:47:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 该死 天哪 - 站起来!\N- Shit. Oh, God. - Get up!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.39,1:47:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别乱动 - 站起来 我看见你了\N- Lay still. - Stand up, I see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.02,1:48:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,听我口令就跑 一 二 三 起\NWhen I tell you, run. One, two, three. Get up.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.02,1:48:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快点 跑 - 嘿!\N- Come on. Go. - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.03,1:48:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,乔伊 拦住他们!\NJoey, stop them!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.74,1:48:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 快点 快点\NCome on. Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.53,1:48:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 你们去哪? 跑这儿干嘛呢?\NHey. Hey. Where are you guys going? What are you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.66,1:48:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没干嘛 - 不 不 不\N- Nothing. - No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.78,1:48:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让我看到你们的双手 - 铐上他\N- Let me see both of your hands. - Cuff him.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.29,1:48:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢 天哪 我们只是... - 我们什么都没干\N- Oh, my God. We were just... - We didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.16,1:48:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,饶了我们吧 我们在草地里找她的耳环\NGive us a break. We were looking for her earrings in the grass.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.12,1:48:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我的耳环掉了 我们在找我的耳环\NMy earring came off. We were looking for my earring.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.21,1:48:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧你耳朵上不是挂着两只吗\NIt looks like you've got two earrings in your ears there.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.25,1:48:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这只 是... 之前的 还有一只\NNot this earring. There was... From before. There was another earring.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.38,1:48:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早些时候还有另一对耳环\NThere's another pair of earrings from earlier in the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.72,1:48:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我认得你\NI recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.18,1:48:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢 天哪 - 你是凯·斯通\N- Oh, God. Oh, God. - You're Kay Stone.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.89,1:48:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没错 我太清楚你是谁了 - 见鬼了\N- Yes. I know exactly who you are. - This is not happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.22,1:48:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让我看到你的手 - 你认真的吗?\N- Let see your hands. - Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.27,1:48:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吧 我回家取个钱包\NYou know, I will go home,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.81,1:48:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,拿点现金给你们 毕竟给你们添麻烦了\Nand I'll get my wallet, and I will get you some cash because we've put you out.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.90,1:48:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拜托 长官 她这就回家拿钱包 给你现金\N- Please, officer. She's gonna go home and get her wallet. And give you cash.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.19,1:48:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有证件吗? - 没 没证件\N- Got ID? - No. No ID.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.03,1:48:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 铐上她 - 别 拜托\N- Cuff her. - No, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.57,1:48:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没证件是吧? 让我搜搜 - 拜托了 别这样\N- No ID, huh? Let's see. - Please, please. No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.08,1:48:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拜托 让我回家行吗? - 少废话\N- Please, will you just let me go home? - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.04,1:48:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你保证\NI'll give you my word.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.50,1:49:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 瞧瞧 真是条漂亮的项链\NWow, lookie here. That's a really nice necklace.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.67,1:49:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去 拿去吧 归你了\NTake it. Take it. It's yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.55,1:49:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,太感谢了\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.17,1:49:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信\NI can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.63,1:49:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你能再帮我弄条项链吗?\NDo you think you could grab me another necklace?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.47,1:49:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你认真的吗?\NAre you serious?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.55,1:49:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你说这些对你没意义 就几分钟的事\NYou said them mean nothing to you. It'd just take you a couple of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.68,1:49:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我才刚消失了半小时 不能上去又马上下来\NI was just gone for half an hour. I can't go up and come right back down.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.18,1:49:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我妈在那呢 - 你刚才给警察倒是挺爽快\N- My mother is up there. - You'd do that for the police officers.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.56,1:49:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢天呐 我的头发 - 我在走廊等\N- Oh, my God. My hair. - I'll wait in the hall.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.10,1:49:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不 准跟着\NNo, you will not.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.69,1:49:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 等等\NWait. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.94,1:49:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\NThere.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.36,1:49:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你真美\NYou look beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.45,1:49:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 你有25条呢\NPlease, you have 25 of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.82,1:49:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,行了!\NFine!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.16,1:49:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 待这儿 明白吗? - 我在这待着 好吧\N- Stay here. Do you understand me? - I'll stay here. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.70,1:49:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别乱动 - 好的\N- Do not move. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.17,1:49:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的\NShit.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.22,1:49:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 很高兴见到你们\NHello. Lovely to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.60,1:50:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 大卫 你好吗? - 挺好 你呢?\N- David, how are you? - Good. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.52,1:50:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈死哪去了?\NWhere the fuck have you been?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.36,1:50:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我想清静一会儿 有问题吗?\NI needed a moment to myself. Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.69,1:50:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道出门还得请示\NI didn't realize I needed a permission slip.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.90,1:50:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我为你操办了这一切 你却让我像个蠢货\NI put this whole thing on for you and you're making me look like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.78,1:50:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪\NGod.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.87,1:50:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 默尔正跟《纽约时报》通电话\NLook. Merle's on the phone right now with The New York Times.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.91,1:50:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.00,1:50:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他找了个排版员正读剧评呢\NHe's got a printer who's gonna read the review.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.46,1:50:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\NMy God.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.54,1:50:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还是说你压根不在乎? - 接通了! 接通了!\N- Or do you not care? - I got him! I have him!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.63,1:50:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢天呐 来了 - 快来 快来!\N- Oh, my God. Okay. - Come, come, come!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.29,1:50:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,来了!\NComing!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.63,1:50:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快点 拿到剧评了! - 来了\N- Hurry, he has the review! - I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.34,1:50:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,剧评!\NThe review!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.71,1:50:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 快点 快点\NCome on, come on, come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.22,1:50:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快来 - 来了\N- Come on, come on. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.05,1:50:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,拉乌尔 凯\NRaoul, Kay.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.05,1:50:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 标题 "凯·斯通回归" 作者罗伯特...\NOkay. Title, "Kay Stone Returns" by Robert...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.40,1:50:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 祝今晚愉快 - 门开着 大家都要下来了\N- Have a good night. - Leave it open. Everyone's coming down.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.61,1:50:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是吗? - 是啊\N- Are they? - Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.49,1:50:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,派对结束了\NParty's over.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.99,1:50:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\NGood night.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.38,1:51:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,派对结束了\NThe party's over.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.63,1:51:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们在赶咱们走 - 什么意思? 咱们才刚到\N- They're asking us to leave. - What do you mean? We just got here.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.17,1:51:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们该在门口拦住咱们的 凭什么让咱们进来?\NThey should've stopped us at the door. Why'd they let us in?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.35,1:51:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰下 你知道凯在哪儿吗?\NExcuse me. Do you know where Kay is?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.10,1:51:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她在楼上卧室 - 好的\N- She's upstairs in her bedroom. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.94,1:52:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 凯在里面吗?\NHi. Is Kay in there?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.40,1:52:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不方便\NThis is not a good time.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.61,1:52:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 但我能跟她谈谈吗?\NOkay, but can I just speak to her?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.40,1:52:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了 现在真的不方便\NAs I said, it's really not a good time.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.81,1:52:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,到年底 如果这人帮你挣了钱 你就留着他\NAt the end of the year, if the guy made you money, you keep him.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.69,1:52:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,否则你就让他滚蛋\NAnd if not, you throw the bum out.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.40,1:52:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰下\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.28,1:53:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 - 你在开玩笑吧\N- Hi. - You gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.16,1:53:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉上门打扰 - 你是怎么进我家的?\N- I'm sorry to disturb you in your home. - How did you get in my house?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.79,1:53:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,请再给我一次机会 我都给你跪下了\NPlease give me another chance. I am on my hands and knees.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.58,1:53:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去日本 还需要1500块参加锦标赛\NI need a ride to Japan and I need $1,500 so I can compete in the championship.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.29,1:53:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常 非常需要这份工作\NI need this job very, very badly.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.75,1:53:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我求你了\NI'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.30,1:53:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我随你怎么使唤 故意输球也行\NI'll work for you however you want. I will lose.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.42,1:53:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,除了让你的活动圆满成功 我没任何个人立场\NI'll have no personal point of view apart from making your event a success.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.09,1:53:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,马蒂 人生没有第二次机会\NMarty, there are no second chances in life.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.10,1:53:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 凭什么没有? - 我给过你工作 你拒绝了!\N- Why not? - I offered you the job and you said no!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.39,1:53:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 那是因为我冲动 我后悔了\NI know, because I was impulsive. And I regret it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.35,1:53:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢?\NAnd?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.65,1:53:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就是我太无礼 太自负了\NAnd I was rude and overconfident.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.27,1:53:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我太狂妄了 态度也有问题\NAnd I was cocky, and I copped an attitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.02,1:53:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,还有呢?\NAnd?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.11,1:53:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,绝不会有下次了 对不起\NAnd it won't happen again. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.94,1:53:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,请再给我一次机会 洛克威尔先生\NPlease just give me another chance, Mr. Rockwell.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.11,1:53:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我任凭你发落 让我做什么都行\NI'm throwing myself at your mercy. I'll do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.62,1:53:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你们怎么看? 我该给这小混蛋第二次机会吗?\NWhat do you guys think? Should I give this little asshole a second chance?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.20,1:53:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拜托 给吧! - 别问我\N- Yes, please! - Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.87,1:53:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道这对我有多重要 拜托 我求你了\NYou don't know how important this is to me. Please. I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.71,1:53:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就让我搭你的飞机 让我跟你们一起去\NJust let me go on your plane, and let me join you there.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.08,1:53:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 我是在低声下气地求你\NPlease, I'm humbling myself before you.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.17,1:53:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 看着你就反胃 - 对不起\N- You're making me sick. - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.59,1:54:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 站起来! - 好的 行\N- Stand up! - Okay. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.63,1:54:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 好吗? 我什么都肯做\NPlease. Okay? I'll do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.59,1:54:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么都肯做? - 是的 任何事\N- Anything? - Yes. Anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.10,1:54:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,行吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.18,1:54:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,顺着走廊走 右手边第二扇门是我办公室\NGo down the hall. Second door on the right is my office.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.43,1:54:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,去把球拍拿来\NGrab the paddle and bring it back here.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.35,1:54:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这比戏里演得还带劲\NThis is more dramatic than the play.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.73,1:54:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 - 确实\N- Okay. - That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.50,1:54:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 马蒂 把球拍给我\NOh, Marty. Give me the paddle.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.92,1:54:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,听好了 我要你这么做\NSo here's what I want you to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.96,1:54:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你趴在椅子上 把裤子脱了\NI want you to bend over that chair and drop your pants.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.22,1:54:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你认真的?\NAre you for real?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.60,1:54:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是个淘气坏小子 现在该打屁股了\NYou've been a really bad boy. Now you're gonna get a spanking.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.10,1:54:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样 你认真的吗?\NCome on. Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:50.68,1:54:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你想去日本的 对吧?\NYou wanna get to Japan, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.14,1:54:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我想去日本 但这就是你想要的?\NYeah, I wanna go to Japan. But this is what you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.23,1:54:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,必须得这么干 趴好\NThat's what it's gonna take. Now bend over.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.48,1:55:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 说清楚\NOkay, so to be clear,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.15,1:55:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你带我去日本 然后再给我报酬?\Nyou're gonna bring me to Japan and then you're gonna compensate me?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.49,1:55:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,明早八点半 拉瓜迪亚机场 咱们出发去日本\NTomorrow morning, 8:30, LaGuardia. We're on our way to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.07,1:55:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我需要票吗? - 飞机是我的\N- Do I need a ticket? - I own the plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.66,1:55:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么知道你会说话算数?\NHow do I know you're gonna honor this?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.25,1:55:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道 因为你没资格讨价还价\NYou don't. Because you have no power here.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.87,1:55:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,趴好\NNow bend over.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.56,1:55:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,手放这儿 弧度要漂亮点\NPut your hands over here. I want a nice arc.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.93,1:55:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,开始吧\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:36.35,1:55:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 天呐\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:38.90,1:55:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 我准备好了\NOkay, I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:42.48,1:55:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这一下是替我儿子打的\NThis one is for my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.99,1:55:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.45,1:55:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这一下是为我自己\NThis one is for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.79,1:55:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,该死!\NGod!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:54.16,1:55:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是加分环节\NNow the bonus round.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.46,1:56:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮的球拍 一面是木头 一面是海绵\NBeautiful paddle. One side's wood and the other is foam.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.35,1:56:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 马蒂 怎么样? - 嘿 泰德 嘿 劳伦斯\N- Hey, Marty, how you doin'? - Hey, Ted. Hey, Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.48,1:56:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 妈的 嘿 伙计 近来可好?\NAw, damn. Hey, man. How you doin'?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.69,1:56:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你看我今晚能住后屋吗?\NYou think I could stay in the back room tonight?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.65,1:56:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 伙计 布莱恩今晚住那儿\NWow, man. I got Brian staying there tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:25.11,1:56:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我本想让你住家里的 但我老婆不答应\NI would let you stay at the house, man, but the wife ain't havin' it.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.07,1:56:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在这儿晃悠到起飞吧\NI'm just gonna hang around until my flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.20,1:56:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪?\NWhere you goin'?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.37,1:56:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,去日本 明早八点出发\NGoing to Japan. Tomorrow morning, 8:00 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.99,1:56:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢耶! - 好样的小伙子!\N- Oh, yeah! - My man!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.75,1:56:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哟 你真要去啦! 弄到钱了 - 是啊 是啊\N- Yo, you goin'! You got that money. - Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.25,1:56:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真为你高兴 伙计\NGood for you, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:39.12,1:56:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你看着一点都不兴奋啊\NYou ain't even look like you excited.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.83,1:56:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没 我... 我挺好的 我挺好\NNo, I'm-- I'm good. I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:43.17,1:56:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,知道你那哥们沃利在后头吧 他一直在等你\NYou know your boy back there, Wally, he's been waitin' on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.51,1:56:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 沃利在这儿? - 沃利 对\N- Wally's here? - Wally, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.93,1:56:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他怎么样? - 沃利挺好 挺淡定的 伙计\N- How'd he seem? - Wally's good. He cool, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.34,1:56:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他就在后头哪待着呢\NHe's back there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.64,1:56:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他看好你 他出一块 她出一块\NHe believes in you. He has a dollar. She has a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.47,1:56:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 怎么样?\NHey. How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.48,1:57:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 哇! 见到你真高兴! 怎么样?\NOh, wow! How you doing? Nice to see you!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:00.98,1:57:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想联系你\NI've been trying to get in touch with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.56,1:57:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢 真的? - 是啊 你的狗呢? 摩西怎么样了?\N- Oh, really? - Yeah. How's your dog? How's Moses doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.11,1:57:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你能别废话了吗?\NYou wanna cut the bullshit?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.28,1:57:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没废话 我是真的关心他\NNo bullshit. I'm genuinely concerned about him.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.07,1:57:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 马蒂 你没事吧 伙计? - 没事 我挺好\N- Marty. You good, man? - Yeah, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.66,1:57:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 听我说 听着 听着 听着\NNow, listen to me. Listen. Listen. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.70,1:57:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你那小妞就在楼下车里 她正等你呢\NI got your girl downstairs in the car. She's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.70,1:57:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈在说什么? 瑞秋在你那儿?\NWhat the fuck are you telling me? You got Rachel?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:17.08,1:57:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.16,1:57:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她跟我说我的狗在新泽西某处 而且你有地址\NShe told me my dog's in Jersey somewhere. And you got the address.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:21.63,1:57:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 - 咱们走\N- Okay. - Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.09,1:57:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,行吧 好吧 让我...\NOkay. All right. Let me, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.63,1:57:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,额 行吧 让我先...\NUm, okay, let me just...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.22,1:57:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,给我两秒钟 我就跟我哥们说句话\NGive me two seconds. I just wanna say one thing to my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:30.84,1:57:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,给你两秒钟行 但老子可不等你\NGive you two seconds, yeah, but I'm not gonna be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.10,1:57:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你要去哪? - 我去哪?\N- Where you gonna be? - Where am I gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:35.06,1:57:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我这就下楼拿榔头砸你那小妞的肚子\NI'm gonna be downstairs taking a hammer to your girl's stomach.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:38.27,1:57:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我要干的事\NThat's where I'm gonna be.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.98,1:57:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 知道了 知道了\NOkay. All right. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:43.44,1:57:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 毛瑟!\NYo, Mouse!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:46.61,1:57:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 搞快点 走 - 好吧\N- Come on. Let's go. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:50.78,1:57:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,父母留给咱们的钱 他的那份大半都被我拿了\NWell, I took most of his share of the money that our parents left us.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:53.91,1:57:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你花了你弟的钱? - 是的\N- You spent your brother's money? - Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:56.41,1:57:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,呵 看来你挺疼你弟的?\NYeah, you love your brother?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:57.74,1:58:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你能给我弟安排个差事 你知道他是个讲究人\NMaybe you could give my brother a job. You know he's a good man.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.04,1:58:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我把你的差事给他 行了吧? 米奇 帮个忙\NI'll give him your job, okay? Mitch, do me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:03.25,1:58:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛?\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:04.75,1:58:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴 行吗?\NStop talking. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:12.13,1:58:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 看到那边的加油站了吗?\NOkay. See the gas station there?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.10,1:58:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,左手边那栋房子就是\Nit's the house to the left.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:16.31,1:58:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 下个左转口? - 对\N- Next left? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.39,1:58:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了\NI got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:37.66,1:58:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,下车 赶紧的\NGet out of the car. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.62,1:58:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,米奇 过来\NMitch, come.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:42.41,1:58:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 鲁本 你看着她 - 噢 好的\N- Reuben, you wait with her. - Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:47.42,1:58:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,老实坐着\NSit tight.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:05.69,1:59:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,搞快点 使劲敲\NCome on. Louder.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:07.61,1:59:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,敲响点\NKnock louder.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:14.53,1:59:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的狗\NThat's my dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:16.70,1:59:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,摩西! 喂!\NMoses! Yo!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:19.08,1:59:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,开门!\NOpen up!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:21.20,1:59:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,操 摩西\NFuck. Moses.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:24.79,1:59:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 搞快点 - 我讨厌那只他妈的杂种狗\N- Come on. - I hate that fuckin' mutt.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.67,1:59:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,摩西!\NMoses!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.55,1:59:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,摩西!\NMoses!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:33.38,1:59:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的狗 摩西!\NThat's my dog. Moses!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:35.68,1:59:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,摩西!\NMoses!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.68,1:59:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧见里头有什么没?\NSee anything in there?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:39.10,1:59:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没 啥也没瞧见\NNo, not really.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:46.56,1:59:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 马蒂! - 妈的\N- Marty! - Shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:49.44,1:59:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,马蒂! 快跑!\NMarty! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:53.99,1:59:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,马蒂!\NMarty!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.03,2:00:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下! 趴下!\NGet down! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:09.00,2:00:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,操!\NFuck!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.97,2:00:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,马蒂! 马蒂! 我中弹了!\NMarty! Marty! I got shot!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:19.60,2:00:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,救命!\NHelp!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:21.35,2:00:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,救命 马蒂! 求你帮帮我!\NHelp, Marty! Please help!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:23.39,2:00:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,救命!\NHelp!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:26.10,2:00:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧? 噢不! 你还好吗?\NAre you okay? Oh, no! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.77,2:00:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还好吗? - 这他妈是怎么回事?\N- Are you okay? - What the fuck's going on?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:30.15,2:00:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 没事的\NOkay. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:31.61,2:00:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我流血了 我在流血\NI'm bleeding, I'm bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:33.53,2:00:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 没事了 没事了 没事了\NOkay. It's okay. It's okay. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.95,2:00:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的很抱歉 - 对不起\N- I'm so sorry. - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:42.66,2:00:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快去拿钱 - 什么钱?\N- Go get the money. - What money?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:43.99,2:00:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快去拿钱 就在他口袋里 在他兜里\NGo get the money. It's in his pocket. It's in his pocket.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:47.04,2:00:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定?\NAre you sure?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:48.12,2:00:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 钱! 就在内兜里! - 好的 知道了 知道了\N- The money! It's in the inside pocket! - Okay, okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:03.18,2:01:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 操\NOh, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.86,2:01:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这什么玩意?\NWhat is this?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:16.53,2:01:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 你这混蛋...\NOh, you motherfucker...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:33.79,2:01:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 好了 没事了 没事了\NOkay. Okay. Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:39.80,2:01:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事? 操!\NWhat happened? Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:44.72,2:01:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,撒开我! 你想上哪儿去?\NGet off me! Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:47.56,2:01:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\Nit's okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:50.52,2:01:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,行了\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:53.36,2:01:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拿到了吗? 拿到了吗? - 嗯 拿到了 拿到了\N- You got it? You got it? - Yeah. I got it, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.57,2:01:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,钱到手了吗?\NYou got the money?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:56.94,2:01:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 钱多吗? - 挺多的\N- Is there a lot of money? - There's a lot.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:59.03,2:02:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你现在能走了 - 我知道 你表现得太牛了\N- You can go now. - I know. You did amazing.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:01.32,2:02:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你现在可以去参赛了 - 我就知道你行 太棒了\N- You can go on your trip now. - I knew you could do this. So good.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:03.74,2:02:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你干得太漂亮了\NYou did such a good job.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.08,2:02:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:07.79,2:02:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 亲爱的 你的预产期是什么时候? - 怎么了? 孩子没事吧?\N- Honey, when is your due date? - Why? Is the baby okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:10.87,2:02:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子没大碍 我只需要你冷静点\NThe baby is fine. I just need you to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:12.79,2:02:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是她丈夫吗? - 不是 我是她朋友\N- Are you the husband? - No. I'm her friend.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:14.71,2:02:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,她还有四周就生了 孩子会没事吗?\NShe's due in four weeks. The baby will be okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:16.80,2:02:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子很安全 现在得说再见了\NThe baby is okay. It's time to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:18.38,2:02:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不能进去? - 手术室只准家属进\N- I can't go? - Only family in the operating room.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:20.42,2:02:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不 别别别别别!\NNo, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:22.09,2:02:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,会没事的 瑞秋 没事的 真的没事的\Nit's gonna be fine. Rachel, it's fine. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:23.93,2:02:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不 别别别! 马蒂 不要\NNo, no, no! Marty, no.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:26.05,2:02:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他就在门外候着\NHe'll be right outside.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:27.26,2:02:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,马蒂 不要!\NMarty, no!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.68,2:02:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞秋 我进不去 他们说我不能进去\NRachel, I can't go. They're telling me I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:30.85,2:02:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不想让你... - 请冷静下来\N- I don't want you to-- - Please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:32.44,2:02:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别走 求你了! - 请冷静点\N- Don't go, please! - Please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:33.94,2:02:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,求你别走! 马蒂!\NPlease don't go! Marty!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:38.36,2:02:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不!\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:48.04,2:02:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢 欢迎来到日本 洛克威尔先生\NThank you very much. Welcome to Japan, Mr. Rockwell.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:49.95,2:02:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢 - 谢谢\N- Thank you. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:19.54,2:04:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,毛瑟先生 毛瑟先生\NMr. Mauser. Mr. Mauser.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:21.34,2:04:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 洛克威尔先生说让你去队尾\NAh. Mr. Rockwell says the back of the line.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:25.67,2:04:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他还不想正式开始\NHe doesn't want to begin yet.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:02.75,2:05:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,该练练了 也该整口啤酒了\NNeeds some practice. Needs a beer.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:06.22,2:05:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,赛斯先生? 赛斯先生\NMr. Sethi? Mr. Sethi.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:08.76,2:05:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 是我 我是马蒂·毛瑟\NHey. It's me. It's Marty Mauser.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:10.68,2:05:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样? 实际上 看到你在这儿我挺惊讶的\NHow you doing? I'm surprised to see you here, actually.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:12.76,2:05:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么说? - 我不知道 我...\N- Why's that? - I don't know. I--
Dialogue: 0,2:05:14.85,2:05:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们确实得宣传锦标赛\NWe do have a tournament to promote.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:16.14,2:05:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 当然 当然\NNo, of course, of course.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:18.94,2:05:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:20.44,2:05:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我该为在伦敦时的表现向你道歉\NI think I owe you an apology for the way I acted in London.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:23.23,2:05:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时就是个混账\NI was a jackass.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:24.32,2:05:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,讲礼貌是基本准则 毛瑟先生\NThere is such a thing as a code of courtesy, Mr. Mauser.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:27.03,2:05:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我知道 只是...\NNo, I know. It's just--
Dialogue: 0,2:05:28.65,2:05:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在我长大的地方 每个人都只顾自己\NIt's every man for himself where I come from.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:30.53,2:05:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是在那样的环境下长大的 懂吗?\NThat's just how I grew up. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:31.70,2:05:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候我觉得自己甚至无法控制...\NAnd sometimes I feel like I don't even have control--
Dialogue: 0,2:05:33.66,2:05:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我对你的借口真的没兴趣\NI'm really not interested in your excuses.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:35.41,2:05:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 知道 这不是借口\NNo, no, I know. It's not an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:36.95,2:05:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 重点是接下来的态度我会好得多\NLook, the point is I'm gonna proceed with a much better attitude.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:39.50,2:05:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便说下 要是今天看到我在场上很无礼\NAnd by the way, if you see me acting rude up there today,
Dialogue: 0,2:05:41.79,2:05:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那是人设 是按剧本演的 我会输个14比21\Nthat's a character. This is scripted. I'm gonna lose 21-14.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:44.67,2:05:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是玩真的 真正的我 那个讲礼貌的我 下周你就能见识到了\NThis isn't a real thing. The real me, the polite me, you'll see next week.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:48.01,2:05:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 下周? - 锦标赛上\N- Next week? - At the championship.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:49.51,2:05:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你不参加锦标赛\NYou're not playing in the championship.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:51.34,2:05:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么? - 你今年没资格参赛\N- What? - You're not participating this year.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:53.35,2:05:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不 我想你搞错了\NNo, no, no. I think you're confused.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:55.18,2:05:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我参加这活动就是为了这事儿 这样我才能付清剩下的罚款\NThat's what I'm doing the event for, so I can pay off the rest of my fine.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:57.64,2:05:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,马上跟我去见洛克威尔先生\NCome talk to Mr. Rockwell right now.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:59.14,2:06:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,锦标赛还有不到两周就开始了\NThe tournament is less than two weeks away.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:01.31,2:06:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 分组已经定好了 - 不 咱们可以重排分组\N- All the bracketing has been set. - No, but we'll redo the bracketing.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:03.81,2:06:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会为一个自以为是的美国人就打乱整个赛程\NI'm not gonna tear up the entire schedule on behalf of one entitled American.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:07.53,2:06:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不 赛斯先生 赛斯先生 听着...\NNo, Mr. Sethi. Mr. Sethi. Look...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:09.74,2:06:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我人都在这儿了\NI'm here.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:10.82,2:06:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你不知道我来这儿费了多大劲\NI don't think you know how difficult that was, for me to come here.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:14.03,2:06:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在可是在日本\NI'm in Japan right now.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:15.49,2:06:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕你走得还不够远\NYou haven't come far enough, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:18.45,2:06:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:19.54,2:06:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你来这儿纯属白费劲\NYou have wasted your time coming here.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:23.67,2:06:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,简直不敢相信\NUnbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:11.30,2:07:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我远渡重洋来到日本\NI've traveled many miles here to Japan
Dialogue: 0,2:07:15.05,2:07:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就是为了挑战我的宿敌 远藤!\Nto challenge my great nemesis, Endo!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:23.35,2:07:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他说什么?\NWhat's he say?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:26.10,2:07:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他不想让你再丢人现眼了\NHe doesn't want to embarrass you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:27.98,2:07:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,让我丢脸? 我早就没脸没皮了\NEmbarrass me? I am beyond embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:30.03,2:07:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他他是个... 你们的冠军就是个骗子和怂包\NTell him he's a-- Your champion is a fraud and a chicken.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:38.08,2:07:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是个怂包!\NHe's chicken!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:41.12,2:07:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,远藤先生同意比试\NMr. Endo agrees to the match.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:43.58,2:07:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好\NGreat.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:44.71,2:07:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,条件是...\NOn the condition that...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:47.63,2:07:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,输家必须当着所有观众的面亲吻一头猪\Nthe loser has to kiss a pig in front of the entire audience.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:51.88,2:07:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 亲猪? - 是的\N- A pig? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:55.22,2:07:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,亲猪? 什么?\NA pig? What?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:57.05,2:07:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他说既然你要表现得像头猪\NHe said if you are going to act like a pig,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:00.51,2:08:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他很乐意帮你配个种\Nhe will happily mate you with one.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:04.56,2:08:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那他妈什么...\NWhat does that--
Dialogue: 0,2:08:31.55,2:08:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这他妈电线挡道了\NIt's this cord in the fucking way.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:33.46,2:08:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我踩到线了 挪开点\NI'm stepping on the cord. Move the cord.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:36.43,2:08:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,把线往那边挪挪 省得我下次又滑倒!\NMove the cord over there so I don't slip on it next time!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:38.80,2:08:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对不起 对不起 - 省得我折了脚踝!\N- I'm sorry. I'm sorry. - So I don't break my ankle!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:50.19,2:08:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,远藤! 远藤!\NEndo! Endo!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:23.26,2:09:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你会说英语吗? - 会\N- You speak English? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:25.02,2:09:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他在说什么?\NWhat's he saying?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:26.27,2:09:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"我们欢迎一位特别嘉宾"\N"We are welcoming a special guest."
Dialogue: 0,2:09:32.02,2:09:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"拉姆·赛斯先生 请上台"\N"Mr. Ram Sethi. Come on up."
Dialogue: 0,2:09:42.37,2:09:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.45,2:09:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,也谢谢洛克威尔先生 举办了这么一场令人难忘的活动\NAnd thank you, Mr. Rockwell, for hosting such an unforgettable event.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:49.33,2:09:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们刚才看到的 只是下周精彩内容的一个预告\NWhat we have just witnessed is a mere taste of what is to come next week
Dialogue: 0,2:09:54.96,2:09:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,届时世界顶尖选手们将同台竞技\Nwhen the finest players in the world will be competing
Dialogue: 0,2:09:58.63,2:10:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,挑战你们家乡的英雄 远藤琴音先生\Nagainst your hometown hero, Koto Endo-san.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:09.35,2:10:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,废话不多说 请出小猪阿古\NNo more words from me. Let's bring on Agu the pig
Dialogue: 0,2:10:13.44,2:10:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这位美国人怎么亲它吧\Nand see the American plant a kiss on him.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:20.07,2:10:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"现在把猪请上台"\N"Now we bring the pig onto the stage."
Dialogue: 0,2:10:42.30,2:10:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 等等 等等\NWait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:46.43,2:10:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿\NHey. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:47.93,2:10:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,亲猪之前 我想先跟他真刀真枪赛一场\NI want to play him in a real game first before I kiss the pig.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:49.73,2:10:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我想跟他真正较量一下\NI want to play him in a real game.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:51.52,2:10:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他 我想来场不掺水的比赛\NTell him I want to play him in a game that's not a sham.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:55.31,2:10:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他!\NTell him!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:57.48,2:11:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你 告诉观众 刚才那是假赛\NYou, tell the audience that was a fake game.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:00.15,2:11:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们刚才是在演戏 我想跟他来场认真的\NTell them it was a sham and I want to play a real game against him.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:02.78,2:11:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我办不到 - 为什么办不到?\N- I cannot do that for you. - Why can't you do that?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:05.12,2:11:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才那是假赛 是排演好的\NThat was a fake game. That was staged.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:08.41,2:11:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没一点是真的\NNo part of that was real.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:10.20,2:11:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我根本没发挥实力\NI was not playing to the best of my ability.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:13.21,2:11:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这是对在场所有人的极大不尊重\NIt was an enormous form of disrespect to everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:16.92,2:11:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 听着 谁想看真比赛?\NHey, listen, who wants a real game?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:19.34,2:11:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,举手示意下 快点\NShow of hands. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:20.71,2:11:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 这位先生 这位先生\NWait, this man. This man.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:24.89,2:11:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,马蒂 你说得对 咱们想看真比赛!\NMarty, you're right. We want to see the real game!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:27.14,2:11:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没错!\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:37.02,2:11:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,远藤 你要站在他们那边?\NEn-do, you're gonna side with them?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:39.65,2:11:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,翻译 翻译这句\NTranslate. Translate this.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:41.36,2:11:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他真要站他们那边?\NHe's gonna side with them, really?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:43.07,2:11:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,任由一家美国公司把他当吉祥物 压榨他的价值卖产品?\NAn American company selling their product off of his back like he's a mascot?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:47.24,2:11:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是吉祥物\NYou're not a mascot.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:48.33,2:11:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱恩 把他带下去\NBrian, get him down.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:49.91,2:11:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们来场真的 观众想看真比赛\NLet's give them a real game. They want a real game.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:52.58,2:11:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 好了\NOkay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:53.83,2:11:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 谢谢 咱们得继续流程\NThank you, thank you. We need to move it along.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:56.00,2:11:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,下周锦标赛我参加不了了\NI'm not gonna be at the championship next week
Dialogue: 0,2:11:57.88,2:12:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,全拜这混蛋所赐 我打不了锦标赛\N'cause of this asshole. I'm not gonna be at the championship.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:00.59,2:12:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,给我个机会 你羞辱了我\NGive me a chance. You humiliated me.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:03.59,2:12:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 求你了 远藤 求你\NPlease, please, Endo. Please.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:05.63,2:12:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拜托了 就当帮我 行吗? - 好吧\N- Please, for me. Yes? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:07.39,2:12:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 太好了 行 - 成了? 他答应了?\N- Yes. Okay. - Good? He says yes?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:08.72,2:12:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他答应了\NHe says yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:09.89,2:12:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 远藤 谢谢\NThank you, Endo. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:13.02,2:12:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他答应了 耶\NHe said yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:34.33,2:12:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这小畜生\NThis little fuck.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:35.58,2:12:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,开干吧\NLet's do this.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:49.64,2:12:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,操\NFuck.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:00.19,2:13:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 马蒂 行吧\NOkay, Marty. All right.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:48.57,2:13:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,耶!\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,2:13:50.66,2:13:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,耶 马蒂! 上啊 小伙子!\NYeah, Marty! Go boy!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:51.93,2:14:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,省省唾沫吧 我知道我拿不到钱\NYou can save your breath. I know I'm not getting paid.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:53.89,2:14:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,赢也好输也好 你一分钱都拿不到 我倒想看看你怎么回家\NWin or lose, you get nothing. I wonder how you're gonna get home.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:56.18,2:14:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你别想上我的飞机 - 没关系 好吗?\N- You're not getting on my plane. - It doesn't matter, okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:58.18,2:15:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你打算取消活动 否则咱们没什么好谈的\NUnless you're planning on shutting down the event, we got nothing to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:00.81,2:15:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你觉得就这么简单? - 对 我就这么觉得\N- You think it's that simple? - Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:03.40,2:15:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来给你解释一下\NLet me explain to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:05.77,2:15:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我生于1601年 我是个吸血鬼 我活了很久很久了\NI was born in 1601. I'm a vampire. I've been around forever.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:11.57,2:15:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,几个世纪以来 我见过很多像马蒂·毛瑟这样的人\NI've met many Marty Mausers over the centuries.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:13.70,2:15:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,有些跟我作对 有些不走正道 他们不诚实\NSome of them crossed me, some weren't straight. They weren't honest.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:16.49,2:15:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,而正是这类人 才能一直活到现在\NAnd those are the ones that are still here.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:18.70,2:15:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你去赢下那场比赛 你也会永远留在这里\NYou go out and win that game, you're gonna be here forever too.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:21.62,2:15:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你永远不会快乐 你永远不会快乐的\NAnd you'll never be happy. You will never be happy.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:26.54,2:15:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 洛克威尔先生\NOkay, Mr. Rockwell.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:38.22,2:15:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,远藤! 远藤! 远藤!\NEndo! Endo! Endo!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:15.97,2:16:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,开始了!\NThere we go!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:05.93,2:17:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈开玩笑呢吧\NYou gotta fucking kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:27.71,2:17:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,赛点\NMatch point.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:09.02,2:19:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别让他逮到你 马蒂! - 耶 马蒂! 上啊 小伙子!\N- Don't let him getcha, Marty! - Yeah, Marty! Go boy!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:52.06,2:19:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:53.23,2:19:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 精彩的比赛 精彩的比赛\NThank you. Good game. Good game.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:55.52,2:19:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个伟大的选手\NYou're a great player.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:58.23,2:20:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你在锦标赛好运 行吗? 希望你能赢\NGood luck at the championship, okay? I hope you win.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:48.20,2:20:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,贝尔维尤医院 有什么可以帮您?\NBellevue Hospital. May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:50.20,2:20:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 是的\NHi, yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:51.29,2:20:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我想找瑞秋·米兹勒接个电话 谢谢?\NI was hoping to be connected with Rachel Mizler, please?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:53.54,2:20:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,您知道她在几楼吗?\NDo you know what floor she's on?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:55.29,2:20:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,额 她应该刚做完手术\NWell, she would have gotten out of surgery.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:57.33,2:20:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你们安置这类人的地方\NSo wherever you keep people like that.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:59.38,2:21:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:01.46,2:21:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,目前看来 她昨晚被转到了产科病房\NSo it looks like she was moved to the maternity ward last night.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:05.30,2:21:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 产科病房? - 是的\N- The maternity ward?- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:07.18,2:21:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- “产科病房”是什么意思? - 抱歉 我不清楚细节\N- What do you mean, "the maternity ward"?- I'm sorry, I don't know the details.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:09.93,2:21:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她还好吗? 孩子生了吗? 离预产期还有四周呢\NIs she okay? Did she have the baby? She's not due for four weeks.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:12.22,2:21:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有这些信息 她是被急救送进来的...\NThis is all the information that I have, that she was rushed--
Dialogue: 0,2:21:15.23,2:21:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,“急救”? 你说什么“急救”? 你刚才还说“转到”\N"Rushed"? What are you saying, "rushed"? First you said, "moved,"
Dialogue: 0,2:21:17.39,2:21:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 现在又说“急救”? - 先生 请您冷静点好吗?\N- now you're saying, "rushed"?- Sir, can you please calm down?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:19.48,2:21:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,直接帮我转产科病房 谢谢\NJust put me through to the maternity ward, please.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:22.19,2:21:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 爸爸! - 嘿!\N- Daddy! - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,2:21:42.84,2:21:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰下 产科病房是在这儿吗?\NExcuse me. Maternity ward's here?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:44.59,2:21:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 顺着走廊走 - 谢谢\N- Yes, down the hall. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:46.17,2:21:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 先生 您得登记一下 - 不 不 我是父亲\N- Sir, you need to sign in. - No, no. I'm the father.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:54.39,2:21:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\NHi.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:37.47,2:22:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了 睡吧 我在呢 我在这儿 没事的\NIt's okay, sleep. I'm here. I'm here. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:42.02,2:22:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在这里 别担心 我哪儿也不去\NI'm right here. Don't worry, I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:44.65,2:22:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,睡吧\NGo back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:46.44,2:22:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:43.62,2:23:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,五号床 谢谢 米兹勒\NFive, please, Mizler.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:01.68,2:24:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我抱抱他吗?\NDo you want me to pick him up?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:22.12,2:24:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,跟爸爸打个招呼\NSay hi to Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:29.59,2:24:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 他在这儿呢 喊爸爸\NYeah, there he is. Say hi.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:42.39,2:24:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 对\NYes. Yeah.
